comments: ["App needs some work on functionality such as location and preferences that aren't honoured. Location should be moved to the top. You're only allowed 3 preferences on the free version and it suddenly disappeared when I got the plan. You get stuck on your 'home' page as there is no navigation to get back to your likes and chat. I figured out i have to hit the back button on my phone to exit the page. Overall, it's a typical online dating experience.", "The app is designed to keep you on, frustrate you into paying, and steal as much data as possible to sell to advertisers. If you pay, the features have some semblance of sense (like seeing who swiped right on you). But that's just typical capitalism behaviour. On a technical level, on a voice only call, turning off your screen ends the call. Going to the home screen and trying to move the preview window around ends the call. And it's too easy to accidentally superswipe by scrolling down quickl", "It is a total waste of time and money. It does not matter if you have premium, you won't be receiving any matches at all (I had subscribed to the premium, still the same). It's like a window shopping app where you just keep scrolling and scrolling until you're satisfied without hoping to get anything. For once I thought this app could be genuine and I purchased the premium, but no, if all I had to do was left and right swipe people, I might have as well stayed on Tinder for free.", 'The UI is quite user friendly. But few things which can be improved on. 1. Message notification doesn\'t pop up a lot of times 2. Call notification doesn\'t pop up ever, plus call drops multiple times 3. Filter option doesn\'t work properly, for example if I choose age range 33-36, I still see people of age 23 4. Algo for common interest can be improved specially for best bees feed, I get best bees who want "Something Casual" while my preference is "Relationship"', 'I can not escape the feeling of a jacked up algorithm. One that puts people on the bottom despite their subscription in some sort of "lead with a carrot" business model. That or no one\'s on this app, and the app does not seem to want to take people who have not been on the app in months in the algorithm. Furthermore, there seems to be no quick, obvious, and easy way to end your subscription.', "I used the app for about one year and had a few decent dates out of it. However, as soon as my paid membership expired, literally overnight, I went from having zero people interested in me to 47, of course being prompted to go back to the paid version. Didn't change location or filters during that time, so obviously, they are manipulating the truth and the end user.", 'For an app that requires access to your location, you\'d think they\'d give you an accurate mileage estimate for people near you, but nope they can\'t be bothered to do that. Just saw someone who lives in the next state over from me and, according to Bumble, they\'re 85 miles away from me. However, when I enter the city on Google maps, it gives me a much more accurate mileage: 156 miles. That\'s a 71 mile difference, nearly double Bumble\'s "estimate."', 'The worst of all dating apps. Like Tinder, gives you options from ridiculous distances, especially if youre in rural areas. Most people are visitors from very far. The worst part is once youve swiped left on a potential match they are removed from your likes and you probably will never see them again."you\'ve missed a potential match" forever. Also they put the location at the bottom so you have to scroll the whole profile just to see the distance factor. Overall a very bad experience', "This app is ok but needs work. I canceled my premium. One of the big thing that must be added is letting me know when the last time a person logged on. That way I'm not wasting time on someone who hasn't logged on in a month. That's a waste of a swipe especially a super swipe. Also need to separate straight people from gay. As I have swiped on the wrong person and they get all offended. If these things were fixed I would keep logging in.", "I have emailed support multiple times about transferring my premium subscription from a previously deleted account to my new account and there has been absolutely no response from anyone in support. Unlike other dating apps that allow you to re-instate previously purchased subscriptions without having to email support (that doesn't respond to you anyway), Bumble just really need to sort its issues out.", "Terrible app! you have to pay for basic Things like just to see who liked you you can only see the people that complimented your profile and that's limited, You have to pay for everything like super swipes & to go back if you made a mistake. They took down one of my photos for going against community guide lines but it's a picture of me in a long dress no nudity nothing inappropriate. & whatever preferences youre allowed to choose (age and distance) doesn't narrow down the field", "Still an awful app, I've tried it multiple times and men never see their related matches. We get search results from 97 miles away from people who don't match our criteria. And you can tell even from the blurry images that you never see the people who actually do swipe on you. It's entirely designed to keep you swiping without any actual results. Don't waste your time", 'Waste of time and money, the location of people is totally hit and miss, when you do "match" with someone it is debatable if they are actually real or generated by the app to keep you interested. For an app that is meant to compliment your social circle/find people with similar interests and so on, no one actually talks. Might just stick with the old-fashioned way!', "All the other dating apps I get plenty of matches, but bumble is awful at what it's supposed to do. No matches, and because of the time limit to message you often miss the matches you do get. Pointless app and a waste of time. Edited, after the reply I received more likes than before after I left a review, strange, then they started to get less and Ive just realised the compliment feature has been removed. I think the free compliments were the only thing that made bumble worth using.", "Because you can't filter results by important categories like religion without paying, the app is essentially useless. You are forced to weed through thousands of profiles that aren't close to your value specifications. The profiles layout is also a mess, listing interests in a buckshot-style jumble where things like children, religion, age, location, etc are thrown into the mix randomly and you have to look around more to find it (those should be at the top of the list).", "I think it's more likely to get struck by lightning and win the lottery at the same time than get a match. It's way too easy to accidentally swipe left, and those swiped on can't come back, and the highlights cost 8 bucks each. Like, who even? Fix your app.", "What's the use of having the dating interface if you can't even contact/connect to a prospect without having to pay a bloody fee? And even then, even if you do want to spend on it, the chances of getting catfished is unbelievably high. The aspect of this side of the app is completely useless. I will give it props if you're using it for business networking purposes and works well if that is your ONLY objective. The dating interface is bonkers.", "it's very picky and decisive wanting you to spend money just like any other app. they shouldn't just give the option free to connect with anyone but they should make a lot easier if you want to say hello or block or do what you would like explicit or not. there's filters for everything. just make it all around app that everybody can use. it's 2023 and this is the longest run on sentence I've ever done. but we all know what we're looking for in the beginning and in the end and who may b in middle", 'It\'s just as bad if not worse than Tinder surprisingly. Customer service is 0/10. I can\'t get a hold of any humans to discuss my problems, I\'ve sent at least 10 emails. I get photos randomly taken down because they "violate" community standards according to the algorithm. I\'ve purchased the lifetime membership twice and, like anyone, deleted and reinstalled the app many times, but now I dont have the lifetime membership, and they won\'t fix it. Summary: All dating apps suck.', 'Bait and switched into "subscription". If I wanted to continue after the 1 month trial I agreed to paid for, I would have chosen a less expensive package. I cancelled the subscription and contacted support 20 minutes after charged, I had to open a PayPal case. 2 weeks later Bumble hasnt responsed. Bait and switch auto-subscriptions are theft. Ive lost $60 to this "free" app and have zero dates to show for it, just "content sellers" posting their Instagram and onlyfans.', 'Totally wast of time & Money, I have not received positive responses from the opposite gender. The 30-minute spotlight feature, promising up to 10x matches, did not help. People seem less active, making it challenging to find potential matches. Considering trying other apps, Bumble has not been useful recently. I do not recommend it based on my recent experiences.', "Bumble is useless without a premium subscription. All filters except age & distance are now locked behind a paywall, so rooting through all the bad matches to find someone is a chore. You only get 24 hours to respond to a match, otherwise you have to pay to rematch. And if you accidentally swipe left on someone you do want to match with, you have to pay to undo it. If the woman matches but doesn't start chatting within 24 hours, (Something that happens A LOT) the match disappears completely.", "Not sure how I feel about it. So far I like how the verification process goes and the app runs smooth but been on it for 2 weeks with premium and not worth it. You don't really get as much people due to the fact that the premium is expensive and also the notification when you do get someone doesn't really appear on either the app notification or email. Also anyone you've liked you can't tell if they even seen the like. Definitely needs more work for the cost.", "I like this app, in my opinion it' s very nice but it's just ridiculously expensive. probably the most expensive app I've tried. so I subscribed in different app although I still use the free features on Bumble. Some things could be better. don't like the fact that only match girls can do first move, think that's silly. I've been on a date with a girl and she complained that men never say anything, then I said we can't, first move has to be from girl.", "When you pay to upgrade and it run out. I have found that when you get likes the system doesn't match you with them. I wants you to upgrade. They then timed out and their gone. Don't pay for the upgrade or you'll just have to delete your account like I did. It should be above all, about finding a connection.", 'Having a limit on likes per day isn\'t a bad idea, but this app\'s limit is almost cartoonish. I can\'t spend more than a few minutes per 24 hours swiping without being told I need to pay 3 WHOLE DOLLARS to keep going. It\'s asinine. On top of that, almost everything else is locked behind paywalls. Though I do like that you can list your pronouns without having to first pick "man or woman." But that\'s just basic decency, not a feature', "I've been on Bumble for a few weeks now. Ended up paying for the boost, matched with someone who, for their prompt, asked me to verify my photo. Prior to this I had tried probably 20 times to verify, and was never able to. Yes I tried photos with just myself. Mimicking the pose, hand gestures, and even location exactly, but couldn't verify. Now I'm stuck on the verification screen, I'm being ignored by the support team. 0/5", "To the pros: fairly clean & simple UI, tho a bit outdated. Cons: gps based search, meaning swiping endlessly tons of people in proximity, including tourists & people in the airport and there's no way to filter out. And you have to scroll all way down to find out person is living somewhere else or doesn't disclose. So looks like tinder at this point and more oriented towards finding one night stand nearby. Exhausting & very disappointing experience for me and after a long time trying it, I'm out", "So there is a subscription model for 21 dollars a month, but this subscription does not come with the ability to see who likes you. For that, you'd need ANOTHER subscription 13 dollars more expensive than the regular subscription. To unlock seeing who likes you, you have to pay 35 bucks a month. That's gotta be an accident, right? Why would this feature not be in the regular subscription?", "Don't buy the spot lights!!!! The app will self activate them and email support stopped trying to help! I tried just not being on for a couple days till subscription weekly one was added when I did log on it has already used it and times out! Yes I emailed them and they tried a couple time but stopped helping. Lost 5 so far. And they are not doing anything to help. Very disappointed in you guys. I'm done I've cancelled the subscription and not trying to get your help when you just blow it off.", "It's...ehhh. My issues are the inability to filter out poly/ENM profiles looking for unicorns, continuing to get likes from men when I am a lesbian, the constant message ads and empty notifications, and the high cost of premium. Been using it for a few months now, met one potential person but I'm demoralized. I won't renew my subscription.", 'I tried several times to get my picture verified, including taking a picture, posting it, and then without moving, taking the same picture in the verify area. They still said I could not be verified. I contacted customer service about it, and my app got stuck on the verify photo page and would not leave that page. I then contacted customer service two more times about it and still stuck. It would be nice to at least be able to try the app out.', "Well developed but core functionality is behind a paywall, and there's no incentive to pay for an app that feels dead. Honestly it looks great but actually seeing who has matched you is behind a pricy paywall, so it's a dice roll as to whether two people see each other, and this makes the limited ability to like people (an otherwise good feature) greatly lower the ceiling on chances of matching. People have moved onto other apps.", 'The app needs work on how it recognizes and interacts with phone media. It\'s difficult to get it to recognize videos & it has double standards when it comes to photos and videos. The app allows the most pixelated pictures you\'ll ever see; however, it won\'t let me upload perfectly fine videos due to "low quality" (they\'re not), wrong dimensions (huh?), or not being shot on my phone (really?). So far, it\'s not very user-friendly.', "Swear this app is a con. I have 9 so say 'matches waiting for me'. I just used a boost and spent the full 30 minutes swiping to see if I would get anywhere with any of them (get rid of or properly match with them) and I didn't come across a single one of these people. It is so blatantly a scam just to make people feel like they have no option but to pay to see more etc etc...", "The customer service for Bumble is absolutely terrible!! I have contacted them over 10 times in a two week span and Bumble has not replied to ANY of my inquiries. My account is stuck on photo verification and I cannot access any othet part of my account. I am currently paying for the Premium option as well. Don't use this app - they dont care about you at all.", "Bought premium (little under $9/wk because it was on sale). Was good at first but right now it's not letting me view profiles of people who have liked me (I can see their picture but when I click on them a blank square comes up instead of their profile). Literally the only reason I bought premium was so I could see people who liked me, so it's very frustrating that the feature stopped working. Hopefully it will work again soon. Edit: also not letting me send or view messages right now. :/", 'Very good idea but poor efficiency; is a pity that girls have only 24 hrs to establish a contact... Also, you should put more filters: for example: eyes color, hair color, etc., and stablish options to search by that criteria; for exemple, if I only want to meet people without kids or blonde girls or short (or tall) girls, be able to find those persons easily.', "The premium option is nice, maybe a little expensive for what you get. My issue is that with the premium subscription you run out of people within your filters. But if you're subscription ends you will run out of likes before you run out of people within your filters. Things don't add up properly.", "Even after having premium it doesn't let's text to someone who liked my profile. It clearly showed in best bees match. But it didn't let me text. What a pathetic app. They just want you to keep browsing and keep paying for super swipes or compliments even after buying premium. You will get nothing here. I think they just got some profiles when they launched the app. Might be no longer active because this app doesn't let people text even after liking from both sides."]

title: Udolly - Dating for disabled
description: Are you looking for a dating app for people with any type of disability? 💙 Do you have someone in your family circle who has a disability and are looking for a dating app for people with special needs? 💙 Are you looking to meet new people near you, make friends, or maybe find love? 😍 Introducing Udolly, the dating app for people with disabilities, whether you're single or a couple looking to make new friends or find love. 🦾 Udolly is the best dating app designed for disabled individuals, including physical disabilities, deaf or hard of hearing individuals, mute individuals, individuals with autism, intellectual disabilities, visual impairments, mental disabilities, and many other disabilities! 🤝 If you have any type of disability and are looking to make new friends or find your soulmate, Udolly is the dating app you need. 🌈 Whether you're asexual, bisexual, heterosexual, or homosexual, in Udolly, you can chat with whomever you want and find what you're looking for. Everyone deserves to fall in love, whether through sign language or any other language 😎. 👌CHAT WITH WHOEVER YOU WANT FOR FREE In Udolly, you'll swipe to get the best matches that fit your interests. Udolly is a free dating application where you can chat for free, without the need for a prior match like in most dating apps... In Udolly, you can find a partner, make friends, and meet wonderful people. You can also chat with thousands of people around the world 🌍 if you wish. ♿️ACCESSIBLE DATES FOR PEOPLE WITH DISABILITIES Udolly is a dating app primarily focused on disabled individuals. Select your disability when signing up, and you'll get the best matches in the swipe. It doesn't matter if you have a physical disability, intellectual or mental disability, if you're deaf, mute, have autism, use a wheelchair, have bipolar disorder, schizophrenia, or any other disability. It doesn't matter if you don't have a disability yourself and it's simply someone in your circle who does. Here, you can be yourself! And live your dating experience to the fullest! 👍. 💌FIND LOVE OR MAKE FRIENDS The Udolly dating app for people with special needs is perfect for finding incredible and charming people. Whether you're into casual relationships, flirting, niche dating like dating for the deaf, militar dating, veteran dating, virtual dates, speed dating, finding love, or seeking serious relationships, Udolly is the best dating app for all your needs 😉. We want to remind you that you're not alone at all 😞! With Udolly, you'll have a chat and dating platform to find friends, flings, or love 😁. 👍DISCOVER THE AMAZING FEATURES THAT MAKE THIS APP THE BEST DATING APP 🚀. 💙 Unique matching algorithm with other users based on compatible disabilities. 💙 Interface adapted to people with disabilities. 💙 Udolly is free and you will be able to talk to any user without having to make a Match. 💙 Virtual dating through calls and video calls. 💙 Listen to her voice in her description to get to know each other better. 💙 Filter by verified profiles. 💙 Filter by your interests: Serious relationship, Flirt, Casual dating or Chat and make friends. 💙 Talk to people anywhere in the world who speak the same language as you. 💙 Find people near you and talk to them for free. 💙 Filter by preferences: What sports do you like? Do you live alone or with someone? Do you have children or would you like to have them? Do you like pets? .... 🔒 WE TAKE SECURITY SERIOUSLY We've implemented some kickass security measures to make sure all the dates are safe and groovy. With features like profile verification and the option to snitch on any sketchy behavior, you can chillax knowing you're in a safe environment. 😃 📱 Grab your free download of Udolly and join our community! Be part of a social inclusion movement that believes social life, love, family, and friendship are key ingredients for happiness! Join the party, peeps!
summary: Dating app for people with disabilty, bisexual, deaf, autism and special needs

comments: ["Very good app overall but there is an annoying bug through all the recent updates where the no Internet message is taped on the bottom of the screen and there's no way to get rid of it and cycle through the tabs. This happens even when the WiFi connection is working. Hopefully this issue will be fixed soon", "It's a pretty good little site but the latest update needs patching with the speed dating it doesn't seem to register people on a regular basis and if you click women only it does seem show any", 'The amount of ads is ridiculous. The UI is mediocre at best. Seems like a quick buck to make at the cost of disabled people. Piss off.', 'The daily affirmations and motivational messages on this app are a lovely addition to the astrology readings..👍', 'Great app for disabled poeple😍 Finally a dating app that works Finding my perfect match, higihly recommend it', "Garbage app. Unless you pay you have to watch a video ad after every 5 swipes. Enfiriating don't waste your time. Edit: Please post your data showing you use 40% less ads tha 95% of the daring apps.", "This is a scam site, you are taking advantage of people with disabilities. You took my money and no matter what no one messages back. Oh look 120 matches and yet no one responds. And the fake accounts are unreal!! I want my money back and I am telling you it's not worth your time or your money. Fake bots or something, also even when you say no to someone they come back as a match. And you can't contact any support it's all a scam!!!! Don't use this app. Also fake reviews. 🤬🤬 Not worth stars", "I don't have any experence because I paid for a subcription and made my profile 100% and verified my email and I haven't been able to do anything😡 rip off. But I will get my money back and report Udolly to the arthoroties for scam.", "I don't know what is wrong with this app I've got plenty of matches and I've made the first move of sending the text, but there's no reply from any of my matches. And here's a tip for all of you guys who are not getting any matches, just do a right swipe first (just one right swipe) than close the app completely and than again open the app. You will find the same profile again (the one which you right swiped before closing the app), than again do the right swipe to the same profile and wa-Lah", "Hello admins. I've tried opening it on udolly via my phone number but my account is suddenly blocked how? I just came to udolly for only 2 days. Please check my phone number d in my account open blocked. I can't buy for 1 month", "Couldn't ever get verified no many how many times I tried. It constantly said I had new likes but I could never look at them. It also constantly wanted me to subscribe when there were only 5 profiles to look at with very little information in them. All of them were super far away too. Super disappointing app since finding someone when handicapped is so hard to begin with.", "There are so many problems I can't cover them all, so I will focus on two big ones: 1. If someone has their GPS off they will show up to people all in the world listed as less thsn 1 km away. 2. It gave me my first match very quickly, but since then I would get notifications for 10+ new likes everyday, but I wasn't allowed to see any of the profiles without upgrading first. Even after 2 weeks both myself and the girl I matched with both didn't have any new matches that we could see.", "Site is glitchy ,can't navigate or access features I received 1 msg and was able to respond ,received lots of likes I can't respond to nor do I know which fake picture belongs to which like . Sometimes the loading spinning symbol spins indefinitely as long as on page and loads nothing . I un installed once and re installed does the same ..", "I live in a major city and theres no one nearby. The app is meh, not the worst but it definitely needs a redesign. Maybe if they made the app more user friendly, more people would join, but I don't see that happening.", 'Fun and easy to use🖐️🖐️', "Won't let you up load a photo from your library unless you grant camera access... this app forces you to grant more permission than it really needs... the app crashed 4 times while trying to create an account... had to start over each time... app isn't designed for ease of use...", 'fun and easy to use....', 'One match in 30km then next one in 100km how is that going to work if your disabled.', "Guys, at first I was happy that someone focuses on the loneliness of people with disabilities. But the app is terrible. Every day I get a message someone liked me, but I don't understand who liked me from the UI, it shows the people I liked. I send messages, no replies. What am I doing wrong? You need a better UI asap. And please improve your scammer detection, yesterday I ONLY saw scammers. You need to better this app as a service to humanity.", "ABSOLUTELY SHOCKING. Why bother? Nothing works, photos don't upload, tried to complete profile but nothing happens. Apparently, my rating is VERY LOW. Maybe it is because I am honest and genuine, it seems fakes and liars prosper. I would be interested to learn how many members are actually disabled. If you prey on the vulnerable , that is wholly sickening and utterly disgraceful.", "Couldn't even upload a picture. This is a colossal mess if you want to call it an app. In my book it NEVER would've scored a 4.8 out of 5 from me, more like I shouldn't have downloaded in the first place.", "Useless app. Wouldn't even let me upload a picture. I tried numerous times with several pictures and it wouldn't do upload them or anything.", 'Udolly is a great dating app for disabled people! The interface is easy to navigate and the community is supportive and welcoming.', "Why is it that this app only brings out the same fake people profiles and can't search or bring out new faces or real disabled people profiles....😠it's really annoying, you people should work on this app please it will be an interesting solid you work perfectly on it", 'The app itself is fine the issue I now face is the sub unfortunately am not able to sub for the month for the 7.99 as it does not give me the option to continue and the device was restarted so any suggestions on what should be done as far as the sub goes', "I was unable to get my account verified and I'm under the impression that that is why I didn't get any messages and was unable to chat with anyone. I tried repeatedly to get it verified but had no success. I am wondering if a new method of verification could be installed or if a new method of verification is in the works.", "I never thought I would find love on a dating app, but Udolly proved me wrong. I've met someone amazing and I'm so grateful for this platform.", "Just discouraged. They say my profile is only 88% done, but the only thing left is they want to know what my social media's are. I don't think that's a proper requirement, unless you want to put that down, your own choice. It's no one's business what else I might be on. So it says my popularity is low...🤔 not very social.", "I couldn't choose my preferences in terms of who I'd like to date,or my birth date. That's as far as I was able to get. However, if that can be fixed I'd like to rejoin and give it a try.", "Bogus app... Mostly users outside of the us. People like supposedly yet never message, doesn't say who likes you without paying... Another scam against the disabled. Deleting promptly.", "I've been using Udolly for a few weeks now and have already made some amazing connections. It's refreshing to be part of a dating app that is designed for people like me.", 'Edit on my previous comment: DEFINITELY a scam. Literally, two minutes after posting it, I suddenly had a "suitor" who wants to chat with me. How is that possible when for every other thing I try to do on the app, it says "Oops, sorry can\'t find anyone right now."? Yeah, I bet you can\'t find anyone right now. Such a hoax. For shame, guys. Why are you trying to play the disabled like that? We\'re disabled, not lacking in intelligence.', 'I don’t know if its only on my phone but everytime I tried to install this application, it says that it cannot install. I’m using android 12 by the way.', 'This app is amazing 🦾', "Uninstalled right away. I tried the app but couldn't get past the loading screen. please fix this", "disabled people don't have the money to waste on random searches", 'Not only is it filled with bots but the filter is useless when it comes to inputting your desires in regards to gow far away you want matches from', "I love this dating app! I think it's great to be able to filter by preferences, it's very different from the others.", "It's fake, just collecting subscription. And it's hard to delete your account.", 'As a person with a disability, it can be tough to find people who understand and accept me. Udolly has been a game-changer for me and I highly recommend it.']

title: Plenty of Fish Dating App
description:
The best dating app to let you really be you and choose how you want to date online. 

Forget the days of awkward online dating and become a POF member, where you can come exactly as you are. We’re here to help you create the same magic online that you would IRL. 

We know online dating isn’t one-size-fits-all, so we let you choose your own adventure and connect with other singles in a way that feels right for you. Whether you’re into spicy dating games, live streaming, or sending a good-old-fashioned DM, we’ve got lots of options to make finding your person actually fun.

What you can do on POF is what makes us different:
      -  Play a dating game and have a laugh while doing it
      -  Search for exactly what you want
      -  Join a stream on Plenty of Fish Live! and meet others like you 
      -  Restrict your first message count so you don't get 1 and 2 word 
        intros
      -  Come as you are and find other real, down-to-earth people like 
         you 

Just click that install button to get started!

POF is part of the Match Group portfolio which also includes Tinder, Match.com, Hinge, OkCupid,, Meetic, The League, BLK, Chispa, Upward, Stir and OurTime.
summary: Plenty of Fish Dating app. Browse photos of singles, chat and date

comments: ["This app has NOT been useful for dating purposes. Also, there are tons of fake asian profiles for some reason. Some users' photos get reused to create fake profiles. The only reliable thing in-app are some of the decent streamers. Suggested improvement: change location of 'Heart' button during streams. It is just above the 'back' button on android devices; and I lost count how many times I exited streams when pressing 'heart' button.....lame. It is like having 'enter' key next to 'escape' key..", "This app gets worse all the time! Just updated overnight on it's own and now instead of a search list it's individual, just to get more clicks on people!? It sucks, and everytime I want a small search radius in a specific area it automatically expands. I don't want to scroll through hundreds of city guys! Also, quit deleting my profile pictures, especially when there are so many out there with cartoon or black images. Not everyone wants their pictures plastered all over the internet.", 'the app keeps getting worse and is actually kind of useless now. also, literally everything needs to be paid for basically & none of it works the search function does not work, i input what im looking for and it just has random woman show up. the nearby function no longer works either, it shows 1 person and is then empty. it gives me a list of "matches" for me and when i click on one of them they are looking for someone different. not worth my time anymore and would not pay a cent to use it.', "Aside from the fact that the amount of gross fake profiles soliciting prostitution sites is ridiculous, they will show you profiles that you can click on but not contact. It's said that these people are looking for something else, which is fine. So why show them in the first place? An inability to go back if you accidentally X a profile is also terrible. All other major dating apps give you this option. Lastly, due to lack of local volume, they show profiles of people hours away. Lame.", "I got 20 likes and am getting likes everyday since I installed the app, but it never becomes a match. Swiping right or left doesn't change the number of likes, it is kinda showing fake likes to convince you to purchase the premium. Update: I purchased the premium. I truly can say more than %70 of the profiles are fake. You can find many profiles with same pictures, some with same descriptions, always shows accounts that are faaar. Do not even waste your time to install it.", 'It\'s okay. Offers more info than the swipe left/right sites. People have an opportunity to make a profile about themselves without a tiny character limit. Issues: Often being shown people not in the same country Inaccurate distance filtering Inability to remove likes(accidents) Should have a hard NO button so that you don\'t see those people again. Seeing the same line up of bad suggestions in you "matches" is annoying. The ability to remove them would be great and make it more accurate over time', 'I am not impressed. I paid premium and thought there\'d be perks but it is a waste of money. Cannot "go back" to accidental "swipe left" when trying to "super like". Cannot message anyone the system doesn\'t find compatible, even if they liked you. Additional features cost extra on top of premium The majority of the blurred messages is just saying someone viewed your profile...as in system spam to entice you to sign up. Not impressed; skip this, find another. Uninstall after premium is up', "The app has seriously gone down hill, the facial verification doesn't work, the help center doesn't work, I can't edit my profile or do anything else and if I have to pay to be able to use those things or be verified to change those things, then it's not worth it. Not when the app is used mostly for hook ups anyways and that's not my thing.", "You can't undo a swipe. Given how many matches are too far away to consider, you get in a swiping rhythm and accidentally swipe the few relevant hits. Really frustrating. The filters are as good as useless - you give an age range and distance and it gives results that are anything but... It also prompts for a review just about every day - that's annoying enough that I'm dropping the number of stars each time.", "The thing I haven't liked about this app is that it hasn't shown women at at a specific age as of my choice anymore. However, it's been showing women's profiles that are older than me even though I limit the age. I believe that people have the right to choose. But the app developers seem not to want that to happen, or that's a bug that must be fixed.", "They completely changed the format to a swipe left, swipe right style and it's freaking awful now! Searches cannot be saved anymore. And with the swiping style you can only see one person at a time instead of your whole page filling up with people. So if you are unsure about somebody you're forced to swipe left or swipe right and are unable to get back to them. 100% chance I'll never renew after my month is up.. they also hide the 1 month option and try to force you to 3 minimum! Never again!", "Recent update has made it completely unusable. No longer a list to scroll through, you need to swipe to add to your list of likes and there's no chance to navigate easily. My age settings seem to not be applied to any search with most too far away and 10 years younger. I'll just delete it I think. There's plenty of other platforms that aren't as tacky as this.", "Rubbish search function (again!). PoF had a very good search: easy to define exactly what you wanted. Then, it was changed to a horrible, Tinder-style: so you can't look through a list & only view people who interest you; now it's time-consuming & inefficient. Then, it changed back (to my relief)...but, now they've changed it AGAIN. I don't know what they're thinking of, but won't be using the site until the old search returns.", "App is broken (again!), search doesn't work, shows people out of criteria, doesn't show if they are online, and only shows an individual profile not a list. Nearby shows only one profile at a time and not if they are online now, recently or years ago. The app had an update that caused this problem a few weeks ago and I think that it was reversed, now they have rolled it out again and it is still broken. The app just isn't worth it anymore, totally pathetic!", 'Absolute garbage dating app. Hands down the worst I\'ve tried. You can\'t set any preferences besides age, and it keeps showing profiles you can\'t like because the person is "looking for something else" or something like that (why even show me the profile then?) And it\'s not inclusive at all. You can\'t be bisexual, you can only choose to seek men or women, not both. There\'s an option to be non-binary, but it does nothing since you have to choose to be shown as a man or woman to people anyway.', "Terrible. It's filled with fakes, as most are. Then you can never cancel. They make you jump through hoops on another website, only that site never works. Only popups that kick you out. Try to contact them and you can't. It just spins you around and makes you give up. Obviously a way to keep their membership numbers up if you can never leave. Overall, just a terrible app.", "I thought it was insulting when the price to upgrade increased by FIFTY PERCENT last year (despite no new features for the extra money)... Now you've ripped the guts out of the app completely with the recent update, effectively turning it into Tinder... Recommended list asides, search/nearby now only shows one user at a time until you swipe left or right (don't be fooled by the store photo on the right end)... Haven't checked yet, but if the web version is the same I'm off to some other app.", "Not good, there is zero help for dealing with troubleshooting and there is no link to direct you to someone with whom you can get in touch, as it just directs you back to the FAQ page. Very glitchy, with features that do not work as intended and the app itself seems like it has transformed into a money grabbing scheme...you can't even view a like without paying exorbitant amounts of money for a monthly subscription service.", 'Search option is almost unusable. Recently online covers the entire UK as best as I can tell, so totally useless. Recommendations suggest people whose preferences specifically exclude you. App is woeful. Pricing is expensive for what you actually get, and the site is almost pointless without splashing the cash. So, absolutely nothing has changed since I was last here nearly a decade ago...except for that god awful colour scheme. Website now just as bad. Would give zero stars if it were possible.', 'Search function is very limited. You cannot remove people from your list of people you like. It is nice that once you pay for the service you can actually see when someone was last online, and if they read your message. Does not tend to attract any quality members. I regret subscribing for 3 months. People can turn off their messaging, which shows an incompatible error when you are using the app, but online it will tell you they shut off their messaging probably because they are getting too many', "It's just awful now full stop been using less and less .the new searching feature is a tinder style swapping of random profiles. Even setting a location distance doesn't work still getting profiles hundreds of miles away. Unlike before you got list of profile with so you was able to pick out the ones that interested you and within your location.", 'At first it was good a few years ago. Allowed a wide range of searching and free messaging. Now its basically like tinder. You cant get a proper list for when you search. Instead its just swiping all together. Then you only being allowed to send one free intro message a day isnt very appealing. As well the live streaming stuff is a major turn off. One final con is that pof doesnt seem to weed out fake profiles from real one even though they added the badge thing.', "Do yourself a favor and skip this app. It's been drastically changed. It's worthless. It auto-edits your searches and changes your results, especially by age and location. Search criteria are very limited to begin with. Since it doesn't let users see everyone they are searching for, matching is extremely unlikely. They do this to keep more people using the app to build ad revenue.", "All of a sudden, when I send messages, they don't appear in my inbox or if it's an existing message, it just doesn't show up. Also I tried to use their contact form in the FAQs, it doesn't populate. I'm trying to figure out why my messages aren't sending? I know everyone that I chat with didn't block me. It also defaulted me back to the original settings. I didn't do that. 2 stars until you fix it.", "Totally horse manure new app. I'm a Premium Member and I want my money back. New features are useless. Search function doesn't work as it won't hold your parameters. Do NOT use this App until they fix it or return to the previous functionality. Perfect example of somebody thinking they are smarter than the world.", 'Used to be free to see who was interested in you now its a subscription fee and expensive too) and keeps showing you profiles for people it tells you itself are looking for a different type of person. If i was able to use the app for its purpose by being able to actually see who was interested without paying close to £60 a month id give it much higher. You charge per week over £10 of that was the monthly cost that would be reasonable', "I'm just going to assume that the developers got money hungry and started to take away features just to get us to purchase premium and it's sad. The app was in a much better state during the COVID lockdown and got rid of a lot of a lot of options that separated from the other dating apps. Also I need a option to be able to filter out trans people because I see way to many of them and I'm searching for biologically natural born women only.", "I'm really not fond of this app. People that hit like are hidden, which then requires a paid subscription, which those options are ridiculous. Seems it just is an app that is out to prey on lonely people. I have no idea, if I pay for it, if the women I'll send a message can even read it, if they're not subscribed too. When you have other apps that don't restrict communication based on required payments, this app is irrelevant. I also have a desired location distance but keep seeing 200 miles", "The app sends you recommendations for a possible match and on some of those recommendations the app also says that this person prefers a different type of person, why don't you choose one of your matches, which is a catch 22 and I don't understand that. Another thing is when you set the distance for looking for possible match the app ignores it and find people a lot further than your preference is said to, again something I don't understand.", "Updates still not good! It's been a while since I was on this site and I was really hoping you would have made better updates. You still lack the ability for users to filter the distance to OUR liking, you still don't allow us to filter for the race WE desire, you still think inside the box when WE want more options that fit US. Please consider these suggestions the next time you decide to make changes and updates. I certainly won't spend money on an upgrade when it's definitely NOT worth it!", "Sign up asks inappropriate questions you cannot skip. Recomends matches that when you click on them say they aren't compatible. Why recomend them then? Even said once that my match wanted people in the same country, despite being in the same country. Should be a great app but these issues and general customer service severely let it down.", "Awful, been on plenty of fish for about 4 years. I hardly get any messages, and if I do it's either a scam job or they stop messaging me for no reason. I even experience sending someone a message, they send one back and not even a day later I will send a message back and it will say profile is unavailable even to paying members or something like that. Also the only profiles they show me are people over an hour away, once in a blue moon I find someone close.", 'Yea, I\'m going to have to take a step back now. Ive been using POF for years, since 2015. There have been ups and downs, like the Live setup, getting bumped down to ONE first contact message a day, and now this new update is just ridiculous. Especially the "Near Me" part. Im sorry to say this but it\'s not a mystery why people stop using POF. It\'s turned into a money grab scheme. I\'m going back to tinder.', "Doesn't accurately show you the people in your area. Search will say nobody nearby all the while I'm being liked by local profiles that I cannot navigate to or respond to, even when it's a mutual match. 1/10 not a good app, new UI makes it even worse", "Some features are nice only when premium is unlocked. The biggest let-down is that while you are looking through these 'plenty' of profiles, most have not been active/online in months. Please add a filter to show people who are active within the past 72hrs or week to save us all time.", "This used to be a decent site but now it's as shady as a lot of others. You can't see who liked you unless you upgrade, you can't send more than 1 or 2 messages unless you upgrade. You essentially can't do anything without a membership. Basic chatting and seeing who likes you should be free and memberships should be for premium options. What a ripoff/scam", "Are you kidding? Limiting people to one new message a day? What's the point in that? When you make a concerted effort to stop the fakes, scammers and hackers then maybe people may pay to upgrade, but as it stands it's not even worth joining let alone paying 😡 11/8/23 the new update is beyond useless. People have stopped using it because the search function is now pointless This doesn't make me want to pay to upgrade, I'm probably going to delete it altogether 😕", "I've been critical of POF for a while. I don't generally use it. Sometimes I check it out. Leave my profile up. See if anyone's ever messaged. No one ever has no. That's typical of dating sites that want you to pay for attention. Not being said their new system where they only show you people 50 km away from you or more. It's a little ridiculous. It says there's a nearby section except for there's maybe three people in total that show up there. Where is it used to be everyone nearby.", "By far the worst dating app I have ever used. It takes way too long to set up an account, I can't figure out how to edit my search preferences, and it will not let me look at profiles when swiping! Oh, and then to delete an account, they dont make it easy to find out, but you have to go to a website to delete your account. If you're reading this, just use hinge or bumble.", "Why has pof changed ? I've limed someone and I can see they clicked like BUT it no longer links you as a match ????? It seems like you've decided EVERYONE has to pay now to unlock matches. The site wasn't exactly great in the first place. And there's no in app support/contact option which is really annoying"]

title: WBYF: Dating For Dogs
description:
WBYF (Wanna Be Your Friend) is the official International dating app for dogs. Join us and be part of a happy dog family.
Start connecting with other dog-lovers in your or any location to match, chat - swap pet photos and go on dates. 

MAIN FEATURES
- Profile for your dog
- Meet dogs near you or around the world
- Private messages
- Vote for your favourite dogs
- Today's Birthdays list
- Find puppies and dogs for sale online
- View Lost and Found dogs
- See if anyone else has liked your profile
- Memory page of dogs (This page is "In memory of beloved pets who went to heaven")
- Go on dog dates

FREE TO USE
WBYF is free to download and use.

CREATE YOUR ACCOUNT
Creating an account is easy! Enter a full date of birth and sex of your dog, then start filling in some basic information to create your profile.
summary: Find friends for your dog around you or from around the world

title: Dog Town: Puppy Pet Shop Games
description:
Start your own Dog Town by breeding and collecting dogs. Experience dogs training where your puppies can learn lots of new commands. Train your dog & puppy, send them to quests and funny adventures. Raise your animals and take care of cute puppies in Dog Town simulator games! Pet your puppy, wash, groom, feed like in real life! Enjoy the cute puppy town with unique pet story & training feature. You can get new dog & puppy cards from pet store for your puppy town & collect them. Discover doggy games and customize the rooms where your dogs live! Design your own interiors with hundreds of decorations that you can find in game virtual store. 
 
In Dog Town you can:
 
★ Train your dogs and teach them lots of tricks with new training feature!
★ Breed and Collect new dogs! 
★ Enjoy gorgeous 3D environment! 
★ Play with realistic Dogs with lifelike behavior!
★ Take care of your dogs: brush, wash, train, pet & feed!
★ Level up your dogs and send them to quests!
★ Decorate your rooms with hundreds of decorations! 
★ Collect more than 100 dogs and more with each update!
 
If you always wanted to adopt pets or any animal, play with puppies and dogs & were interested in animal shelter, pet & puppy rescue then this is one of the best virtual games for you. Grow your littlest doggo and have fun grooming them . Each animal has a unique character and behavior, so you will always recognize your "Sleepy" from the "Jumpy"! Also you will see their unique behavior while training your puppy. We've put a tremendous amount of effort to ensure that you would feel attached to your animal dogs just like you would to the real ones.
 
In this dog & animal simulation game you can collect dog breeds like: Basset hound, Staffordshire Bull Terrier, Springer Spaniel, Boston Terrier, Labrador Retriever, Australian Shepherd, German Shepherd, Yorkshire Terrier, Bull Terrier, Great Dane, Schnauzer, Cocker Spaniel, French Bulldog, Pomeranian, Doberman, Siberian Husky, Miniature Pinscher, Beagle, Chihuahua, Corgi, Dachshund and other dog breeds. After training your puppies they will become stronger & will participate in more challenging quests. There is a large emphasis on Dog Collection and management for casual and midcore players. 
 
Download now and start having fun with cute pets!
 
 
Enjoyed Dog Town? Join our community:
https://www.facebook.com/groups/382045606113476
 
Please note! This game is free to play, but it contains items that can be purchased for real money. If you are having any problems in the game or have a great idea about it please contact gamesupport@frismos.com
summary: Cute doggy rescue story, pets & animal care game. Dogs shelter hotel simulator.

comments: ["The game has a cute style for its models: a satisfying semi-realistic approach. I was curious to see what the game could offer, however I basically wasn't able to get any further than naming my dog as the game freezes upon nearly any action afterwards.", "This game is an absolutely amazing game that works on and offline! I love this game the dogs are Soo cute and it takes like 3-4 minutes to get four puppies!!! This game does have some things that cost money though like the exclusive pack. But I still suggest that you get this game because it can entertain you for hours if you let it! Wonderful game for road trips or long plane rides! Setting it up doesn't take long. Download it today!!!", "This is a great game, for kids, teens and adults!!! Though this game is fantastic I almost have all the dogs, maybe making a cat version of the game would be super cool!!! Just a suggestion I'm sad I almost have finished the game ):", "Back when i was a kid, i always used to play this game, and it was so much fun! The old classic dog game. It has no annoying ads, but this one? It had alot of ads, for every quest, every oven, every tab there is an ad, and if i watched an ad for a free pack, it wasn't working now! I watched an ad, but i didn't receive the rewards. Look, i know the effects of the pandemic caused alot of downhill to most companies, but please, maybe reduce the amount of ads? It's ok if no,iunderstandwhyyoucouldnt.", "It's a fun game and it has cute dogs but I don't like the random ads that pop up and the fact that after you breed and spin the wheel it still shows all the dogs you already have but other then that it's fun to play.", 'Super cute, so many nice animations for a free game. Not many ads at all. But the game keeps crashing unfortunately.', 'Well this game is really fun but it can get a little boring 💤 but it is interesting there are different types of dogs and u can breed them and u can feed and brush and bath the dogs well I totally recommend this game for u well tgats all 👋.', 'Very fun it confused 😕 me at first but just click on the brush treat and sponge 🧽 icon to do it but it is fun to breed and 👀 see what you get. They look so realistic.', "I love this game the dogs are so cute but when I tried to buy more room to put my dog in the room it took my money but it didn't give me more room at all and it happen twice and sometimes there are pop up ads and it does get bothering after a few time", "I get many of the same ads and that gets very annoying but other then that it's a very fun game in my point of view yall should check it out", 'This game is cute, but it does get a bit irritating sometimes. Like, a helping guide would be useful, explaining the purpose of every single thing in the game. Training of the puppies is also confusing. They will move quite rigidly. The puppies need more movement flexibility. Kindly do something to make the game run like butter because it is the only cutest game of puppies, and I love it.', "It's a lovely game, but the ads are really obstructive and annoying. I dont mind an ad every like, 20 mins or so but I'm literally getting them every 5 minutes and each time I get them the game crashes. Please sort the ads out and it will make the experience much more pleasant. x", "Holy Ads, this game is unplayable! Ads every 30 seconds, it's insane!!", "I love this game its fun and so cute what I'm not happy about though are the constant ads and having to pay 8.99 a week for subscription to drop ads and get perks. It's too expensive for a game on my phone.", "I love this game it online but it's fun because you can decorate furniture And you can collect puppy and feed them. They will grow big and you can pet Them.", "This is an amazing game to let off steam and it is exactly what I needed, but there is one awful problem with this game. I deleted the first time I got it because my phone was clogged up, but then I tried to re-download and it had deleted all of my progress. I was on one of the highest levels which I worked extremely hard to get, and now I have to restart which really puts me off. This game would without doubt be 5-stars if it weren't for this annoying mistake. Please fix this 🙏🏻.", "I love this game I got so many dogs and it's kinda hard but the dogs are so cute 😍 💓", "I love this game I play it all the time! But now whenever i start the game it doesn't let me in, it says an error has occurred. But besides that (it won't let me in no matter what I do) it's still a good game, oooo adding a newfoundland and irish wolfhound would be awesome!", "It's unfortunately quite buggy. I think it's a super fun(ny) game and would love to play more. But I can put in a lot of time's work which includes watching a bunch of ads (which makes you money) and when I come back, all of that work will be undone (dogs are unleveled, my tokens are gone, etc). May have to uninstall if it persists.", "This game is awesome but it takes forever to load like when I first got it,it loaded fast but I've had it for 2 week's now and it kinda changed so when you get in it takes forever and then you get into the game and this is why I gave it a 4 star rating I hope this helps.", "Just like fun because it's cute seeing alot of puppies running around", 'This game is fun lol I love dogs, but there is some ads', "I really like this game, but I think there are too much ads and bugs. the part that i think can be improved: 1. There are too many ads, like when you want to move room or when you want to collect food (without doubling it). Maybe it's better if you put ads just to get rewards. ex: for packs or speed up things or respin 2. When i watch ads to get double food, it's become 0 not double 3. I think this game is good for children, but some ads in this game is a bit inappropriate for children. Thanks", "Only played this for another game, but not even twenty minutes in I had it uninstalled. The game itself is pretty good. Great animation, adorable dogs, and it's not glitchy too. However, I can't deal with the amount of pop-ups that take up the entire screen—all of which you can't exit for ten seconds each. I understand that you might need the ad money, but how about giving us optional ads for boosts/speed ups or something. I'm pretty sure so many others are also annoyed by these endless ads.", "It's a good game, really, but I wish there were more things to train the dogs. I feel like we should be able to train working dogs' service dog tasks and things like that. More things related to the breed of dog instead of all of them being the same.", "Logged into the game just fine but there is no dog and I can't go into the little dog store to get a dog cuz they're all locked I went to every section on everything on the screen that I could and could not figure out where this dog is someone please explain to me if I'm doing anything wrong", 'I breed my dogs but then when i come to complete the breeding it like the breeding never happen but when you try to find the dog . It say it still is in breeding . 6 of my best dogs are supposedly still in breeding but when I hit the nest it just gives me the option to breed again .', 'I really love this app as it is a dog game I thought this was not good but turn out to be great! 💯 The dogs breed is alot! I really like that Totally worth to trying to get Ur dog in the game my dog is a shi Tzu and there is in the game thanks that is totally extra credits for the dog town game recommended', "This is the best game ever. There aren't excessive ads, you can get diamonds easily, you can get gold easily, and the dogs are adorable.", "I absolutely LOVE this game! It's fun, adorable, and it teaches young children how to take care of dogs! I love how there are no ads. 10/10 would recommend.", 'Been playing the game for a while and enjoy it. I like the ample opportunities to earn diamonds and money. This is refreshing in comparison to other games that make it nearly impossible to obtain either without spending real money. Thank you. The game is a little glitchy with the dogs either running in place, jerky movements, moving too fast. You may want to iron these glitches out.', 'This game is great! It is a great app to show parents that you can take care of a dog, or for fun! I love everything about it, however it is slightly buggy .. an add pops up sometimes during the tutorial and it still gives me the tutorial but no option to close the add so I have to do it by guessing where everything is. other than that, Awsome game!', "This is a really bad game I mean u can't even enter it 😞. For the first time before I entered it I thought that it'd be sooo fun but I couldn't even enter it. It's really just a fake game😒😕. Soooo not fun 😕. If there was an option I would give it zero stars 😒. I really wish that I could play this game.", "Love the game, but it's pretty glitchy. Graphics are great, there's always something to do, real money isn't needed to advance, it's a cute and addicting game that all ages can enjoy. I do wish there was more you could do with the dogs though, like an outside yard, go on exciting walks, dog clothes choices, i also wish breeding was a little more genetically accurate as well, and i wish that the dogs were more size-accurate. All in all, it's a 10/10 with room to improve 😁", "I love this game. It's pretty, cute, friendly and intuitive. One that even the older can appreciate and help them relax. I just think there could be a way to make it less visualy stressing (with a high number of visual elements on the screen later on, with tons of quests pilled and all that).", 'I like it but I wish they had a Foxe dog in the game thanks for listening', "It's a really fun game and I sure do enjoy playing it. However, there is a few issues I have come across. It has way to many glitches, it freezes a lot and it sure does have to many adds. The glitches that it is having...the dogs when they move all of a sudden it's like ether the dogs or the game are freezing.", "This is my favorite game and I will love this game forever good job on making this game I can't wait for games just like this KEEP UP THE GOOD WORK!!!", "I love everything about this game except for spinning the wheel when you have a love story. I literally spun the wheel 10 times in a row watching an ad between each spin to try to get a different breed and more than half the time hit the same exact breed and color for one I already have. This has been a consistent problem and generally makes the game frustrating and not fun to play. I've considered uninstalling multiple times because of this coding choice and now I'm done unless it's fixed.", 'Nice game but too many ads and too lengthy. Mostly at least 30 seconds. Why watch a static company logo or black screen for 30 seconds? Even when you claim something, ads comes out. I understand the need for ads, however ads should be 10 seconds at most. Too much time wasted on ads cannot really enjoy the game. Will rate again if improved.']

title: BringFido Pet Friendly Hotels
description:
Looking for a pet-friendly hotel? How about an awesome dog park, trail or beach? BringFido is the #1 trusted resource for dog owners looking for the lowdown on the best hotels, attractions, and restaurants that welcome pets. Our app brings the best of the website to your phone, giving you free on-the-go access to pet-friendly information worldwide.

Our new app makes booking a pet-friendly hotel easier than ever. Search hotels near you, and sort by distance, popularity, rating and price. Traveling with a large dog or more than one pet? Use our filters to find hotels that welcome big dogs and multiple pets. You can even narrow results to browse hotels that don't charge a pet fee! With the BringFido Pet Friendly Guarantee, our customers are assured of finding the best pet-friendly spots available. Get instant confirmation of your booking, and, if you have a question, you can always call or email our team of Pet Travel Experts.

Find nearby attractions, upcoming dog events, and local resources such as dog walkers, groomers, sitters, veterinarians, and pet supply stores. Don't see your favorite place listed? Use our app to post a new pet-friendly location and share a photo of your dog enjoying his favorite spot. Browse our dog photo section and share pics with your dog-loving friends. You can even leave reviews of your favorite pet-friendly attractions.

Download the BringFido app today and use the coupon code FIDOAPP to save $5 on your next booking.
summary: Find great hotels, attractions, and restaurants that welcome pets.

comments: ['Concept for the app is wonderful. However, it needs the ability to search by specific addresses and to sort by distance closest to the address searched. You can only sort by city, which forces you to open each and every location to find out what the address is. Then you have to put the address into google maps to find out exactly how far it is to your location. It makes using the app to search for a restaurant to go with your dog very tedious. This is especially a problem in big cities.', "International users beware! Overall. It's easy to use and saves having to search and filter to find pet friendly hotels. Biggest fault that is very disappointing is that the prices are in default USD and do not change to your local currency, in my case CAD. Nor does it list the price as $$USD, just $123. Once you find the currency select button at the very bottom of the front page then you can select the correct currency. It will also book and charge in USD unless you select the currency.", 'Needs GPS locations. it\'s great for finding hotels, parks and trails but really needs to show current location on a map so you can see what\'s nearby instead of having to click on every listing. Again, when doing an initial search, should be able to click on a *near me" rather than needing to enter the town/city every time', 'Great but could use some work. When searching for hotels you have to reset the filters every time you get done looking at a hotel and if your comparing places it can get really frustrating and annoying. Other then that the people are great and and the app is super helpful in finding a place that takes dogs especially large or multiple dogs.', "The UI doesn't let me input a specific location or range and keep it. For every single search, I have to add it. It's annoyingly grating and ticks me off, esp since I have to go back and use the hamburger menu just to get back someplace. Even though you can add cats to your profile, it's for dogs only. Moreover, this app is utterly useless if you're not in a major metroplex. There is NOTHING near me. I have no idea why ppl suggest it here bc there are zero results.", 'I love your app, but I wish you could make it easier to add new locations. Perhaps having the ability to pull in names, addresses, phone numbers, etc. from Google Maps might help a lot. I have started adding dog friendly locations a few times, but I give up because of the inconvenience of looking up everything.', "Love Bring Fido! We have used this service for multiple cross country road trips with our four Anatolian Shepherds. i have never had a problem finding a hotel or activity, and the customer service is great! The Android app has some issues though. More often than not, I get a server timeout error and can't do anything. Thankfully I can rely on my laptop to access the desktop version.", "I haven't used the app much yet, as my upcoming trip is fully planned but the app is easy to use and friendly with a clean design. I would like to know if there is a way to change the currency from USD to GBP, I also had a little trouble uploading a picture for myself or the hounds. Overall good app, but I hope for some guidance on the currency :)", "This review is based solely on using the restaurant portion of the app. App is extremely laggy when searching in map mode or just crashes all together (using pixel 3 w/ Android 11). Half the places that pop up are not actually dog/pet friendly. A Google search and a phone call would be easier and save you the headache of showing up somewhere that doesn't allow animals. This app needs a ton of improvement. Until they fix these issues, this app doesn't save you any time finding pet friendly places", 'Easy to use and accurate search results. Every hotel they list does allow dogs, but not every hotel allows dogs in every room, which makes sense. The description of services and pet fees is accurate. We enjoyed using this app during a 3 week long road trip and it has proved priceless. Have not yet booked a stay through the app, as we are gun-shy of third-party booking services, but we will try it out on our next trip. Kudos to the BringFido developers!', 'Great idea! But lacking. It would be great to have a "current location" option on the first screen. When traveling you aren\'t always sure what the city or town is named. I also wanted to post a picture of the place I just reviewed, but it seems the pictures are more general rather than related to the specific place.', "The app works well but it doesn't use your location and everything is default to US$. There should also be a sort function. Places show up in random order, not even by distance.", 'Used this app on a 2600 hundred mile trip !!! I found out the hard way that when you let a 3rd party pay for the hotel there is no way to get your money back for a subpar hotel . Also found out they do not fiscally check out the hotels and rely on feed back or what the hotel says . We ended up at a couple really questionable and unsafe places ! Used the app after the incidents to find places and called directly to ask question . And when we got there we had the option to leave .', 'Worthless when the restaurant/brewery "pet friendly" recommendations are patio only. Should at least be a filter. What\'s the point in 3/4 of the year when patios are closed? If you\'re looking for hotels only, every single site offers that filter. Pass on this app.', "Works sometimes, but if I want to search restaurant in a certain zip code area it suddenly doesn't show any places. So you pretty much have to manually look at everything with the map that glitches out. It's all just long and tedious to use this app, when Google maps is easier.", 'Completely useless search function. The search function does not recognize major airports as search destinations. Booking, Expedia and pretty much any major travel site does a far better job of locating let friendly hotels.', "Amazing customer service!! I highly recommend their concierge service. I traveled across many states with 5 small dogs and each night I would call Brinfido. Then, they called hotels ahead of time asking if we were okay to book. Once confirmed that the hotel would take us, they made the reservation and always in nice hotels. Upon arriving at the hotels for my reservation, I had no issues checking in, but Bringfido always gave me a name of the person that ok'd our stay in case I did have issues.", 'This is a phenomenal service! The folks that answer the phones at Bring.fido have always been extremely helpful and friendly every time I have interacted with them with a question regarding a pet-friendly hotel or in making changes to a reservation. Using the app is a breeze too.', "A client had recommended this app to me years ago and I've been using it since, especially when I travel. Customer service is A+ and booking places to stay (not just hotels) is so quick and easy. It's a fun way to discover new restaurants as well. I highly recommend this app if you're like me and need to have your baby always by your side.", "They farmed my room fee out to Expedia. Expedia's credit card declined. We spent 1.5hrs in the lobby exhausted with 3 dogs. Got hung up on several times. They wouldn't refund me so I could just pay the room myself. Come to find out, I paid 15.00 more for the room than if I had gone to the hotel myself and purchased it. Sadly, I can't recommend them to anyone.", "I've used bring fido half a dozen times now and have loved it every time. I don't have to read through small print on other hotel websites to find out if our 2 large dogs will be allowed. I just set the filter and search. So easy!", "Bring Fido is my go to when I'm making travel arrangements. Always found places that allow us to travel with our large dog. My only complaint is on occasion it redirects you to other sites to make final bookings instead of booking through the app (which I prefer to ensures that the hotels/place I book with are aware I have a dog).", "I was thrilled to discover they have an app, too. I've done a dozen bookings with them over the years and never had a single problem. Travel planning with a big dog like ours can be filled with doubt and anxiety. BringFido alleviates those issues for us by doing all the hard work. The only way BringFido needs to improve is by us users being more diligent. RATE HOTELS AND WRITE REVIEWS!! Don't just book and be on your way. So many hotels have few or no reviews. Reviews improve the community.", 'I love being able to select from pet-friendly accommodations without the guesswork. You can also save hikes, attractions, or even articles to revisit later.', "No GPS. The map doesn't remember your location when you go back to it and has to reload which the requires you to redo your more specific location search. About half the restaurants I've looked at are permanently closed and one that's open requires you to leave your dog outside the premises.", "If you have a dog and go anywhere, this app helps a lot. it's cut down the time I spend searching ahead on my phone by 70%at least. also, it's incredibly easy to book through the app. five paws way up.", "This app is a must if you travel with pets! Easy to navigate with an option to book through the app. There's no other application as useful as BringFido.", 'So far I love this app. It makes finding lodging that accepts two 90 lb dogs much, much easier than other search apps not focused on specific pet friendly restrictions. It also specifies additional pet fees along with the nightly rate.', 'DO NOT USE THIS SERVICE We booked a pet friendly hotel through bring fido. At confirmation they say "Our Canine Concierge will make sure you’re assigned to a pet friendly room now, so there won’t be any unpleasant surprises at check-in." We get to our hotel and it\'s NOT PET FRIENDLY. They were completely unhelpful and left us with no room. Now we have to wait days for our refund and have to book another hotel with money we dont have! No, they are not. Youre app does not uodate policey changes.', 'I love the app, I just used to find activities and restaurants and so far all recommendations have been excelent. I used to look for hotels but I preferred to book directly with them but the Bringfido recommendations have been so useful.', 'BringFido is an amazing site. There staff is knowledgeable, friendly and helpful. I use them for all my trip planning. The best part is there is no fee like Vribo or Expedia.', 'We just got back from a two-week roadtrip through nine states with two dogs (Chihuahua and Aussie-poodle mix). We were totally dependant on this app and it was awesome.', 'Great for finding pet friendly hotels, often with much better than expected prices! I have always been pleased by what I find on BringFido!', "Cool app but when I try to save things, it wants me to login and will only do so from a web browser. What's the point of the app if all it does is direct me to a web browser?", 'Every single property I click on does not show up. The only ones that do are way more expensive than what is advertised. Deleted. Typical bait and switch, as usual.', "I like the service but there needs to be a number to call to actually speak to someone if your reservation is not at motel. This is happening to me at this moment. Money gone and no reservation. Maybe you guys should not charge until we arrive. I'm expecting a full refund as I have to make other arrangements", 'one star off for not providing a geolocated search feature, and another for not being able to customize the navigation app. however, overall, I do like this app.', 'great app for traveling with your dogs. reviews are very helpful. helpful staff for same day bookings, which is often how we roll. never sure what you may want to stop and see on the way!', 'Basically just a web search in an app, I wish that it had any kind of location function or a rest stop rating system.', 'We stayed at the Seabird Lodge in Fort Bragg. It was dog friendly but the room we reserved was not available, it was under repair. The only reason we made reservations there was the room had a patio. Instead they put us up in a room without patio or porch. It was unfortunate we were not notified ahead of time, we were only 4 hours away. For what we paid for the room and condition of the room I would not recommend this to anyone.']

title: Pet Perfect - Puppy & Dog Care
description:
Recognized as one of the Best Apps of 2022 by Google Play🚀

Embark on a Journey to provide the best care to your Doggo 🐶.

Get easy to follow, daily schedule of activities, curated by experts.

As a dog parent, we know you are tired🤔 of wasting time looking for info according to your pets age & breed. It’s hard to keep a track of their daily key activities like feeding, walking, bathing, brushing, etc. Many a time you can’t remember the vaccination & deworming dates📅. Don’t know what steps to take for your doggo’s perfect upbringing? Because your pet can’t tell you what they need! We seldom seek the opinion of experienced Pet Parents & Veterinarians. But in reality, we need one place to learn all the best dog health care practices.

Pet Perfect is your one-stop companion for everything you’ll need to make the most of your furry friend. The best companion for your pets, curated with love and passion😇.

🐾Pet Journey- feature provides pet parents with step-by-step tasks on every stage of dog life according to your dogs age and breed.

🐾Pet Engagement - Have fun with your furball with our vivid range of perplexing dog sounds🔉

🐾Vaccination & Deworming Tracker - Get automated reminders for your dog's vaccination and deworming dates with just a single tap. 💉

🐾Dog Community - Get your queries resolved by Experts and Veteran Pet Parents & make new friends who share our love of doggo🐕.

Check our website here:- https://www.petperfect.in/

Also, do follow our Social Media Handles:-

Instagram:- https://www.instagram.com/petperfect_ig/

Facebook:- https://www.facebook.com/petperfect2021

P.S. Currently, we support the following pet types: Dogs
