comments: ["I have been using the app for a few days. This has a cute and simple interface. There are useful information and also a community where you can ask your questions. However, the major problem I faced was when I opened the app recently the app first page didn't show up instead it wrote formatexception:unexpected character and asked to tap to retry..after too many tries still the pages don't show up.", "Thanks for this 😊 i am very happy to use this this app helping me to train my dog very easily thank you very much this is very interesting I can easily use this just love it keep ti up 🤠😉 but now I having too many problems like i can't read all the guide he says that I need to get a subscription whyyyy", "It's an Amazing App. It is a perfect solution to my pet parenting problems. I used to forget health check-up and vaccination date. I used to blame myself for delays. But Pet-perfect allows me to automatically manage my health records. The Premium is worth it. Thank you pet perfect for making my life easier.", 'I love the app, so much good information, and I especially love the reminders. As someone with ADHD, it makes life 10x easier to know that this app keeps track of EVERYTHING I need to do for my puppy 🥺 My only suggestion is a way for families, or couples to connect pet accounts so that they can keep track of the care together!', 'very very helpful and informative instructions are really helping to raise a puppy without any hesitation', 'Really good app especially for new pet owners.would absolutely recommended it.at first it blew my mind', "My name is Denita and our Instagram handle is @_.labradore._ We're totally in love with this pawsome app. Indeed a great help for pet parents especially first timers. It is so easy to access the guides given in the app, you can find the solution of almost every concern through them. The vaccination reminders are also of great help. Really appreciate the hardwork of the creators and the team behind it. One thing that I would like to have changed is that we can only ask one query in a day.", 'Your app is perfect except that when I try to get into app it shows " UPDATE APP". Which I couldn\'t, I tried uninstalling and reinstalling the app again, which was of no use. NOTE: THIS APP DOESNT HAVE AN UPDATE IN PLAYSTORE. How do I update it?', "My name is Shikha and our Instagram handle is @eskiego I want to say that I love this app. It makes pet parenting so easy with all the activities reminders, vaccination and deworming reminders and a wide range of guides which help to understand our furbabies' behaviour perfectly. In today's busy world, this app is the most necessary thing so that you do not miss out anything and take care of your fur baby in the best possible way.", "Really very good app, but as the name says, I think it's missing other types of pets, at least cats, in addition to dogs. Please take as a suggestion to update this wonderful app. I have two cats and my puppy, so I miss information about my cats as well 😻🐶", 'Amazing App. THE PERFECT APP FOR PET PARENTS. I love the app.❤ In the App, there are Health records, Activity reminders, Expert Guide and the most important PET COMMUNITY where u can ask Questions and get Answers from EXPERTS. Thanks for the Amazing App.🤗', "My Name Is Priya and our Instagram handle is @thejessijr i want to say that i love this app. It makes pt parenting easy with all the activities and reminder vaccination and deworming reminder and a wide range of guides wich help you find Your Furbabys Behaviour perfectly. In today's busy world this app is the most nessessary thing so that you don't miss out anything and take care of you pooch in best possible way ✨❣️", "amazing app... just an additional suggestion..personalized diet chart timings and suggestions is something I felt missing according to my dog's health, weight and age.", 'Very easy to navigate through, and super informative!!! A must-have for all pet owners.', "Love the detailing in the app. One stop solution for all my pet needs. It used to be such a hassle earlier and now we just gotta get on the app and it's done. Thank you devs.", "Amazing app for both new and experienced pawrents! It's gold out there. Just what I had been looking out for since I got blessed with my first furbaby. 🐶🌻", "It's a very informative and a helpful app, keeps me updated for my pet's vaccines and medications if any. Totally recommended.", 'I am delighted to say that the information on each points are very useful and helpful for the parents of a GSD. Many many thanks for sharing such an excellent and informative post. With best regards. Asit Kumar Sau LL.B, WBPS. Deputy Superintendent of Police, Retd. Advocate Belur Bazar, Howrah. West Bengal.', 'This is a very informative app, with all the related information needed like vaccination info, health-related info, etc. This app is highly recommended to pet parents.', 'Amazing app with all the features details & best part is all the guides are very scientific & personalized for my dog 🐕', 'Very useful app for a pet owner. but irritating notifications many times a day.. had to block from phone settings', 'Amazing app for pet parents. Amazing and informative guides helps me a lot . The interaction of pet parents helps to clear all the doubts and problems. ❤️ Would give 5 stars to them', 'I\'m not able to sign in. It shows a message in snackbar saying "Sending OTP failed!"', "Every pet owner must have this app this is an very good application to maintain our pet record's as well as the knowledge given in this application is very good.", 'Good app the wikis are helpful vaccination schedule really eases things very helpful for modern pet parents like me', 'Best for may dog breed . try this app best app forver . 😍😍', "It's an amazing app....one stop shop for all your needs.", 'Informative, Helpful and Reliable. 👍🏻', 'Whole profile have created then so many times app will updated ... So bad Experience...not gud', 'best experience with this app', 'very helpful app for those who raise pets at home। thank you.', "It's very helpful App for Pet Owners , it intimates our duties of taking care of our pet's .", 'Very nice app and platform to discuss the dog related issues with a very good community', 'This app is very good app i can read all about puppy care and ask any question in this app i just want to give more stars but there are only 5 great app goo and install now', 'after updating feeling difficult in searching to update vaccination , deworming', 'One stop destination for all the pet products', 'Very great app. Best for any pet parents!', 'Useful & easy to understand', 'I have paid for this app but it is still showing upgrade', 'Nice App must download if you have a Pet.']

title: Dog Sweetie - My Puppy
description:
【BEST IPET ON YOUR MOBILE DEVICE】
★Best mobile game of the first China Mobile Internet fist award.
★Excellent game of China app game contest.
★Top class dog raising experience. Virtual dog for everyone. 

【Main Feature】
★Breed collection: More than 30 breeds in the game, even Tibet Mastiff included!
★Dog care: Feed,water,bath,touch.anything. you can even hug your dog!
★Tricks training: Teach your dogs to learn more than 20 tricks! Even including Gangnam style!
★Top class DIY: Dress your dogs, Decorate your house, Give your dog tattoo.Best of all,you can try everything before you purchase them.
★Interaction: Interact with friends, help them or steal their coins,your choice.Get married and have puppies.
★Challenge: Fight on the street to earn the ranks. You have No.1 dogs.Bravo!

【Contact】
★Support：support@lonfun.com

comments:
['A buggy mess. It logged me into someome elses account, and wouldnt register any gold i picked up, so the dog i apparently now own will forever be sick and hungry. Jarringly weird would be a way to describe it, and thats without even going into the empty microtransactions Hell that is this game. Definitely not worth even trying, its that busted.', "Installed the game, it took me to someone's account. I tried to log out and get my own account but I'm legit stuck in this account the game will not delete the account info from my phone.", "This game looks adorable and I'd love to play it but I can't. It crashes anytime you try to open the app", "I can't even do the app. It's just A gray screen. I do not recommend playing.", "This is the first time downloading the game and when I hit start to start the game, it loads someone else's account that is named Hannah! I am not playing this game that someone else purchased!", 'I love it would like more clothes and more toys like pull ropes and tennis balls for in the house and maybe if we can feed them of wifi', 'Couldnt even open the app. Crashed every time.', "It's good but when I installed it, it logined me into someone's account. Please fix this.", 'Game kept crashing before I could even start.', 'The game wont let me report a user whose been asking me inappropriate questions and at one point had an inappropriate picture. Could you please fix the report button?', 'Unable to play because crashes', 'I love the game but we res cat sweetie I miss it', "My account get hacked? Didn't login for few months, now I open it and my account became others. My dog disappeared. What happen", "I'm not sure if this is related to the game My Dog??? Or is it a direct copy? Please advise! One star for now-", 'I DONT GET WHY PEOPLE RATE THIS SO LOW!!!!! THIS GAME IS AMAZING + MY DOG WAS A COPY OF THIS BELIVE IT OR NOT. YA, THIS IS THE ORIGINAL MY DOG GAME BRO', "sucks, won't even load..", 'My dog is find but she is very good when i call her she run to me😍😘', "I'm love animals game", "Why the heck am I on someone else's account?? Fix this!", 'Logged me in someone elses game', 'What happened to dog sweetie and friends', 'I DONT LIKE IT', "It takes me to someone else's account.", "It won't let me play anymore it says I need to update it but I just downloaded it AnD tried to log back in", '作为一个小学生，第一次接触的手机游戏就是心动小狗，玩了两年，然后玩我的世界去了，下载回来的时候发现游戏名不一样了，更多的东西要钱了。不过为了回忆，我就不打算删除了。', "This game is really cute and fun but it has a lot of problems connecting to 
the WIFI, and I don't know why but it never let's me put my own profile pic 
in it. Please fix these two Problems then I'll think about giving 5 stars 
😕😦", 'I love this game and all the cute breeds but I wish I knew how to get diamonds without having to buy them but all in all I love this game.', 'So I would like to speak to one of your workers because I think I was 
hacked on my game 3 minutes ago', 'Ooh I love this game so much because whoever made this game is SUPER good 
at it...love dogs play this game...', 'I really enjoy this game it helps me get ready for me to have a real dog and its really fun it has all the different types of dogs its unbelievable', 'I like this game you can mate on it', 'I loved it because I love taking care of dogs!!!🐕🐕🐕', 'The best', 'I wish it would delete in it', "I think this is a very great game. You can have a variety of dogs and you can talk to people, and it's just very fun. The two reasons I have a 4 star rating is beacue 1. It's super hard to get diamonds. 2. Almost EVERYONE on the game is Chinese, and I know it's a Chinese game, but I can't talk to anyone. Iwouls like for more English people to play so I have people to talk to. Also, it's should not be that hard to get diamonds. Please considerthe diamond change and let's all have a fun time together. If you would like me as a friend on DogSweetie, my name is AussieBoss.", "Dogs Sweetie is my favorite game that involves taking care of dogs and them able to have puppies. The graphics are really cute and realistic. [The puppy's howl I'd super cute.] After I got a new phone and I wanted to get a game that includes dogs and puppies and this was my second choice. Although my first choice, I realised, was less developed than this game, so I went with Dogs Sweetie and I didn't regret it. They helped me recover my account from some time ago. Though I must say, this game does require a lot in order for your dog to have puppies, requiring the intimacy and 12 skills, which in order to learn a skill, your dog needs to become fully mature, will take quite some time.", "I love this game and dogs but can you add an update to this I really want my dogs back and I lost my account an update what I'm thinking was to use ur code to enter your account I would really want that so please update this", 'I love the game 🐕🐕🐕🐩🐩🐩🐕🐕🐕', 'Cute little dogs', 'Fun&cute']

title: Dog Scanner: Breed Recognition
description: The Dog Scanner app will identify your dog's breed reliably in just a few seconds! Besides taking a picture, you can also record a video or upload an image from your gallery. Got a mixed breed? No problem, the Dog Scanner app also recognizes mixed breeds! We provide you with detailed data and interesting facts about the different breeds of your mixed breed dog. No dog around? Doesn’t matter! The Dog Scanner app also recognizes humans: Simply scan yourself, your friends, your family or the people around you and find out which dogs you resemble the most! ------ NEW! Become a part of our Dog Scanner community! Share your results and compare them to the results of the community! Upload pictures of your favorite dog to our Social Feed and share them with other dog lovers! Have a look at the profiles and photos of other users, like and comment on posts from our dog community and filter them by date or popularity! Additionally, you can easily share your posts with your friends by simply sending a picture directly from the Dog Scanner app. ------ NEW! Catch all dog breeds and become an expert! Catch all the dog breeds with our Gamification feature – just like in Pokémon Go! Master the challenges, earn virtual treats and become a true dog expert! Compete with your friends or users from the community and climb to the top of our ranking list! ------ All dog breeds in the Dog Scanner app! The Dog Scanner app currently identifies more than 370 different dog breeds, including all breeds officially recognized by the Fédération Cynologique Internationale (FCI) and even some more! Our comprehensive database with information and pictures of all dog breeds (including the unofficial ones) can also be accessed completely without scanning! Give us feedback on the Dog Scanner app! Let us know if the dog’s breed has been correctly identified. If not, you will get useful tips to improve your own results. If you also indicate which dog breed is in the picture, you help us to enhance our software since the app automatically learns how to provide even more accurate outcomes. Also suggest or vote for (unofficial) dog breeds that you want us to add to the app in the future! Get your premium upgrade! With our premium version, the app will no longer show ads and your results will be available faster. Furthermore, you can now choose whether your dog breeds should be recognized rather quickly or with higher accuracy. With the premium version, scanning dogs is also possible in offline mode, so you no longer need an active internet connection to identify their breeds. With the optional in-app purchase of our premium version, you will also help to support this app. ------ Find us on social media! On our social media channels we provide you with the most beautiful dog pictures from the community. You will also find many interesting facts about man's best friend. Furthermore, we will keep you updated on all new added features of the Dog Scanner app in the future. * Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/dogscanner_app * Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DogScannerApp * Twitter: https://twitter.com/dogscanner_app ------ Just give it a shot! Dog recognition as easy as it gets! Despite the small app size you will get all features and be able to identify a dog’s breed or get access to our extensive database at any time! Before you consider getting an expensive DNA test, simply scan your dog with the app and the dog breed will automatically be determined within seconds! Download the Dog Scanner app now!
summary: See a dog, but don't know its breed? Just take a picture and find out!

comments: ["The app itself is not bad as a bit of fun, although suspect it isn't very accurate with mixed breeds. The number of ads makes it unusable though, as there seems to be one every 20 seconds and if you close one of the small ads, a full page one immediately appears. I may have purchased the ad free version if I had a chance to try the app for a bit longer, but am not prepared to watch that many ads just to decide if I like it.", "To say the ads are intrusive is an understatement. Every action you take gets an ad and the interface is similar to those websites that have 30 download now buttons trying to get you to download a virus. The TikTok ad is app-breaking. It is unskippable with no X to click. Even opening it still takes you back to the ad. There's no way around it but to exit the app. I did manage to get one picture in and it identified the breed incorrectly. Why would they think we'd pay for a pro version? 0/5. ;(", "I got the perfect shot and it correctly identified the dachshund in my dog. It all just depends on the perfect shot (all you have to do is just take a side picture of your dog looking at you helps). It just should lower the analysis time and have a better accuracy when people take pictures of the owners dogs. But I love it even if they didn't do that.", "actually surprised me! sometimes it fails to identify a common breed but then somehow it manages to CORRECTLY dentify random cross breeds. obviously the picture will play a part in how accurate the results are, but even a perfect pic might not get the right result cuz obviously identifying a breed by a pic alone isn't an exact science and one dogs can look like one think but be 100% proven to be something completely different, appearances can be misleading. cool app though", "I would definitely recommend this app. Out of all of the apps I tried, this one was bang on identifying a 4 week old puppy we rescued. the accuracy isn't 100% but pretty damn close. For anyone using this app, make sure you use more than one picture to see how many times it recognizes a specific breed, and then do your research. This is a great app to use to give you a lead on a breed, and the rest is up to you.", "Not sure to give it 2 or 3 stars. They did well to get 1m downloads so respect for that because it's main functionality which is the scan is average at best. They even openly admit on the app that the top 1 accuracy is 71%. This is a pretty bad result. If you like bells and whistles then this app is for you. If you would like to get proper identification - there are better apps around.", "1-27-21 App problems have been fixed. Great job! Update 9/27/20-Developer updated app. When scanning photo(s) from gallery the app no longer works properly but constantly flips back into camera mode. Unfortunate. From 5 to 1 star and deleting app. Will check back periodically to see if it's fixed. 7/31/20-So far, a truly wonderful and innovative app. I'm really enjoying it.", "Fun and pretty accurate readings based on a photo, or many different photos together to cover all bases. It was right on on my dogs and has a lot of info on specific breeds. I scanned many different photos of my dogs and it gave me the right answer with details on breed, or breeds. Very cool and fun. I was glued for over an hour playing around with this app. I don't think I'll delete it yet.", "This isn't a bad app at all. I've only used it for about four of my assorted mongrels so far, but it knew my hairy Bulgarian dog was a mix of various Eastern European shepherds. I don't know her origins, but the dogs it suggested seemed pretty close. Plausible enough for passing curiosity, anyway. I wouldn't want to settle an argument with it, but it's a bit of fun.", "Its something different and some what funny. But very unreliable. So unreliable that I am willing to bet it get's the dog breed every time unless ypu owm a pure bred. Again I am not hating the app or developers. Hopefully they can creat default ways to take pictures this way it is more accurate. Especially when considering am entire skeletal structure in a picture.", "the free version is nearly impossible to use bc the amount of ads. I mean, I've never seen anything like it. Waaaaaaaayyyy too many ads. pretty much every 3 click activates the same Temu ad for a washing machine 🫤", "I love it! I've been waiting to find something like this for years It's pretty spot on. I think it's cool that it can recognize mix breeds. I can't say for sure how accurate it is because my dogs are a mix of at least 2 but probably 3 or 4 different breeds, but the app results agree almost perfectly with our best guesses for both dogs, so i think it's great.", 'Absolutely awesome and how do you do it? I was very easily able to scan several dogs in our family (must sit still 5 seconds) with the app. The answer is perfect especially for Heinz 57 and somewhat mixed breeds. It gives a breakdown in percentages with sample photos to support their analysis. Suggest you take a FULL profile scan and not facial close up. Highly recommend this app!!!', "Pretty cool app. Just wanted ideas of what my dog could be mixed with as she looks like a larger version of a heeler. The only negative is the intensity of the ads. I'm fine with free apps showing ad banners, or occasionally a short ad, but press ANY button and you're stuck with a 30s ad video AND the post-ad promotional poster that makes you wait to press the 'x'. Good for a one time use it if you have patience, or probably if you pay", "I kept being interrupted by ads, and when I finally reached Dog Scan, there was nothing...NOTHING to show me how to use it!!!. It also crashed 3 times while I was on there. Don't bother with this app, its annoying and VERY frustrating!!!😡😡😡", 'If you give it a reasonable photograph, it does seem to come up with reasonable matches. I tested three mixed breed adult dogs of unknown origin, but from the same litter. One of the three looks different from the other two. The app gave me the same sorts of answers for each dog. Dutch shepherd. I tested multiple photographs. The variation was not as great as I expected it to be.', "It's a good idea, but it's not accurate; It seems like developers are on the right path as far as using images submitted and asking users to correct what breed the scanned dog actually is for future recognition abilities of this app.... but it has never been right :/ I tried multiple dogs that I know.", "Could be useful to rescue groups and shelters. Best results when using a full view picture without much else in the photo. Not useful for some mixed breeds. Others have provided good feedback. I've tested some shelter dogs, comparing their guess to the tool suggestion. Many times I've agreed with the app over the shelter guess.", "The app is pretty good so far. The only time I can say for a fact it was wrong was when I scanned my rat terrier. She's a runt and sickly, so she looks more like a chihuahua. It scanned her as that, but it's a common mistake, so not one that surprised me. Aside from that, it gave me good insight on what my other dogs might be. Only issue is that the video ads can be intrusive. Went from one every 10min to 3 in a minute.", 'I have 2 poodles. One everyone thinks is not a poodle due to the texture of her hair. The scanner guessed both breeds correctly. I see complaints about the ads but it comes with the territory of a free app. Stop complaining or pay for the premium version.', "Dogs don't like loud sudden ad sounds in their face while getting a photo taken. These adds are full-screen and can't be backed out of. Unexpected startling ad sounds is not too smart for a pet friendly app.", "I had an incredibly loud and intrusive ad and it had no obvious X or mute, pressing what looked like an escape route forcefully opened my app store, once I went back to the app, the advertisement was still stuck on my screen, now it had an X and I pressed it, but it took me right back to the store again. Double kill. I don't think I trust this app and I'm deleting this immediately, it couldn't correctly identify my dog either.", "This app is pretty cool not to sure how accurate these kind really are. I took a picture of one of our dogs and got my friend in the picture and it kind of confused the app so it gave me an idea to take a picture just of my friend & the result was partly correct when it said human the very funny thing was it said the larger percentage was Great Dane. We laughed so hard. I still smile when I think about it. They do say sometimes we tend to resemble each other-thing is we don't have a Great Dane.", 'I have three foster puppies from the same litter, all were totally different. Also, took different pictures with same outcome. Different breed, every time.  Also took another picture of my dog (we had a dna test on him) again with different results that were completely different. It’s a good thing the app is free.', "It doesn't seem very accurate because I scanned my dog at three different angles and I got three different results and two of the same angle and two different results and not one of the breeds, out of all the five times I got results, did any of the results have one of the same as the others. So I couldn't even get a good guestimate.", 'I was impressed. scanner is most impressive. was able to get clear and focused images of dog scanned dog three times and he was identified as the same breed each time and the percent of account increased each time until 98%. Yes GREAT APP. 👍', "It's so cute! But besides that, it's fairly accurate so long as you do several photos from different angles. Sometimes depending on the features that certain breeds have, a weird angle could change the entire results.", 'Great fun! Used this app on my "pavement special" rescued dogs and came up with some interesting results. Not that accurate, but I won\'t hold that against this app as dogs can be difficult to identify, especially if they are bouncing around when you try to scan them - something the app manages to do well. Like I said great fun, informative on breeds and I enjoy using it.', "The app has been correct. I clicked incorrect on one of them because the husky breed was off but that's not a surprise because the breeds are so closely linked. a second scan of the same dog with body without the face came up with the closer mix. I'm very impressed and happy with the results. I also love the info that comes with the breed.", 'As someone else said it\'s good for entertainment value. App said my purebred Mastiff (rescued retired breeder) was Mixed breed and gave FOUR different breeds, most of them pretty off. Apparently my other 2 rescues are both Australian Kelpies, one of them a purebred - don\'t think so. [EDIT: have to eat my words - I searched black/tan kelpies and my "purebred" rly matches the look!] Using the app was nice enough (except for the ad every single time). It just doesn\'t have superb accuracy. Yet?', "it's kinda fun. I'm not sure I would pay for the app but it's fun to scan my dogs and see what it comes up with. I believe it scans the dog then runs the photo through its database of pictures and compares it to them. it pulls out the ones that look most like the dog depending on the angle of the scan you did. The first scan I did of my 3mth old puppy seemed pretty accurate. I will be trying my other dogs too. It also has a cat scanner option.", "I've only just downloaded this, but it correctly figured out the breeds of all three of my dogs, even from images where they weren't facing the camera, and figured out that my cat was, in fact, a cat when I tried to trick it. Now, none of those would be hard for a human to figure out, but I am genuinely impressed an app could manage it.", '4 and a half stars Nifty little app. I love animals, especially dogs, so I can defnitely see how having dog scanner will come in handy. Whenever hanging out with family and/or friends you can turn it into a fun game. Knowing dogs as well as I do I can see myself winning a lot, lol. Not only do you have the fun factor of playing a game, its an educational tool as well.', "Love, LOVE, L-O-V-E this app. and, I haven't even had it for 24 hours! I have been using a similar app, for several months. Yet, so far, Dog Scanner is, Leaps & Bounds above the competition. I mean, you guys are...KILLING IT! Period. I purchased the premium version of Dog Scanner. Main reason was to eliminate Ads. (Thanks, Ads-No-More). I was, also, impressed by the amount of, factually accurate, breed specific info (contained-within-the app.) Kudos-to-You, Dog Scanner. Your product ROCKS!😋🙃😜", "This app is interesting, and insightful. I've only tried it with my dog, which was an unknown mix of breeds until I used this app. Very fun and surprisingly accurate for how many poor angles and lightnings I used in the pictures. The ads in app are very small and do not get in the way of using the app (thank you!!)", "I tried 4 different photos of the same dog, all clear pictures that included his face. (The dog is a stray mutt that showed up.) Results varied widely. Side views of the head seemed to work best. It doesn't work that great with mixes, but is still helpful in that it can suggest possible breeds present in the ancestry of your mutt. Then you can google those breeds specifically to see more pictures. Easier than combing thru photos online, but not as good as asking your vet, is my opinion.", 'Just downloaded the app, from one I saw so far it seems excellent. Obviously ads all the time....normal. What I would like to see is improvement on detailed info..like weight range and longevity. For me this seems like an excellent app for people who see a dog they like and interested in getting one, so providing this kind of information would bring greater interest in your app.', "Awful app. Ads whenever you press anything, can't figure out how to close the ads, cluttered and too complicated. Waste of time.", "Highly Accurate - Don't listen to the naysayers. Often times when people get inaccurate results, they are using a bad picture with bad lighting. This app has accurately identified over 100+ breeds as I volunteer at an animal shelter and have used it to identify both purebred and mixed dogs. Whenever it got the breed wrong, changing the angle of the pic, adding better lighting and finessing the overall picture - resulted in a correct identification of the mutt at hand. Enjoy! A great app indeed!!", 'Really cool idea for an app. One thing that would make the results higher quality would be to allow users to upload multiple photos from different positions, then run each photo through the service and average the results.']

title: Tinder Dating app. Meet People
description: With 70+ billion matches to date, Tinder® is the top free dating app, and the best place to meet new people. Are you looking for true love? An open relationship? Are you looking to get out there and find a date, or do you just want to make friends and chat? With Tinder, you can meet local people everywhere and get the best out of your dating experience: Whether you're straight, gay, bisexual, or anything in between, Tinder allows you to be who you are and find who you want. Share your interests and learn more about your matches to get the conversation started, and get the sparks flying. Photo Verified Profiles: Because the only surprises we want are flowers on the first date Video chat: Test your online dating chemistry and meet new people from home! Traveling somewhere? Get to know the locals from around the world. Dating in New York, meeting new friends in Miami, or going on a date in London: Wherever you go, we’ll be there. Some people call us their “most dependable dating app”, some people call us ”the world’s most popular free dating site”, but you can just call us when you want to meet up with people in your area. Match, Chat, and Date. That’s our mantra. It’s easy and fun to meet new people on Tinder®. Make your profile stand out with your best pics and a little something about you to increase your match-making potential. Use the Swipe Right™ feature to Like someone, use the Swipe Left™ feature to Nope. And no pressure: With our double opt-in feature, the interest has to be mutual in order to be a match. How many dating apps can say that? While you’re here — make a toast to the Gold life and enjoy some of Tinder’s premium features with our Tinder Gold™ subscription ♥ Likes You — see all your fans, saving you precious time ♥ Unlimited Likes for you to catch feelings for as many new people as you want ♥ Rewind — undo your last Like or Nope ♥Passport — find people online outside your zip code ♥ Monthly Boost — put your profile to the top for thirty minutes to get more attention ♥ 5 Super Likes available per week Looking for access to all of Tinder’s premium features? Join Tinder Platinum™ to also get your Likes prioritized with potential matches, to be able to message before matching, and more. There’s a plus side for those not ready to commit to a relationship with Gold or Platinum. With Tinder Plus®, you’ll unlock features including Unlimited Likes, Unlimited Rewinds, and Passport. So what are you waiting for? Download the best free dating app today! It doesn’t matter if you’re looking to make friends, meet new people or find your perfect match, Tinder is a place where everyone can find exactly what they’re looking for. — and it’s about time you showed up. ----------------------------------- If you choose to purchase Tinder Plus®, Tinder Gold™, or Tinder Platinum™ payment will be charged to your Google Play account, and your account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Auto-renewal may be turned off at any time by going to your settings in the Play Store after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during the active subscription period. If you don’t choose to purchase Tinder Plus®, Tinder Gold™, or Tinder Platinum™, you can simply continue using Tinder for free. All photos are of models and used for illustrative purposes only. Privacy: https://www.gotinder.com/privacy Terms: https://www.gotinder.com/terms

comments: ["The app with the most users I think, but so many bug's on it.. So annoying. Not receiving notifications when someone message me, or receiving a notification, but nothing when I open the app to see it. Trying to show which song I love most on Spotify, but you can't actually do it. It only shows random songs that I don't even listen to, or listened it once lol. Lots of tiny things like that that makes to overall experience not so good.", "Latest update has changed UI for the worse, bunch of pointless borders around stuff that do nothing but consume screen real estate. They've also disabled the ability to zoom photos by dragging down on them like we could do in previous versions, so when users have poorly cropped / zoomed-out photos where you can't see them, now you can't make them easier to see. It also seems like every update makes the blurred cards of recent likes even more blurry, to the point that they're now useless.", "App went from something pretty decent to an app where you have to pretty much pay to date almost. Daily superlikes have been removed and instead weekly superlikes were added. Even if you pay the ridiculous amount for platinum you don't even get much out of it. On top of everything, even if you change your preferences to disable push notifications for everything except messages and matches you'll still be met with pointless messages to remind you that you can still swipe randomly 3 times a day.", "App works fine most of the time, but today became super glitchy. Said my account was terminated, then i rebooted Phone and now it wants picture verification but the buttons aren't working. Frustrating waste of time. Too many fake profiles, and no option to report them. The app is doing nothing to try and give you any tools to figure out who is actually real and who is fake.", "Very glitchy, one of its biggest draw backs is that it doesn't send notifications consistently at all. Or sometimes even update that someone sent a message within the app. So you will realize you accidentally ghosted someone like a week late, and by then they are rightfully usually not willing to keep talking. It's very buggy and causes a lot of problems.", "1 star edit: Came back to try again after a breakup. Got plus for the unlimited likes and I have not had one match... not one. I'm a good looking guy and know how to be charismatic, so this just baffles me. It's like it won't show me the people the app is telling me are swiping right on me so that I upgrade my subscription, which is around $50 a month. I have had infinitely more success on bumble so far, for free might I add. This app is complete garbage now. Avoid at all costs.", "Another pointless update where the design is changed to the disadvantage of the user. Before, you could highlight a bio and run it through a translator and translate it into English, for example. This is no longer possible. Furthermore, the new design is simply more colourful. It's as if the UX/UI team has been dismissed and replaced by 1st semester students. The people responsible should either rethink their quality standards or be replaced. Non of the last updates improved anything.", "A great idea in principle, but seems to either not be working as intended, a lot of fake profiles, or could even be site generated profiles to keep you active/ interested. I've had push notifications of matches and messages, and there is nothing on my contacts. I've matched and messaged, and had no replies. I've tried reinstalling the app, several reboots and still no better. I am not a gold member, but from what I have seen so far, I would not pay to upgrade.", "The location is extremely lacking on profiles. I have to use a map app to ensure profiles are actually in the state as I've had several searches day a city and that they're 10-20 miles away and they are in another state! Sometimes across the country! It would help if they put not only city, but also state in the location. The distance can also be fixed for better accuracy.", "Bugs that haven't been fixed for years (like when you accidentally super like someone and undo it you still don't get the super like back). It's obvious the app is not made to find a partner, but only short term hookups. The whole app is made so that you should just keep coming back to it, pay for more and more functions, over and over again, forever. Tinder is made and controlled by very, very, very evil people, but their abominable karma will deal with them eventually, of course.", 'Piece of junk. It seems impossible to get even a single match. After going through the stack once, any new entries are junk. No profile. Can\'t see face. Cynical. Not so much a problem with the app, but it\'s a miserable experience. User profiles are bare bones. There\'s a list of "Passions" that you can choose from, that really don\'t make sense. You can select "Atari" but not "Video games." You can\'t write in your own. There\'s minimal selection for who you\'re interested in. Man/Woman, age range.', 'Don\'t pay for it. It\'s a cool app, but there is a glitch with the premium features under Likes You. If you add any filter to the Likes, it restricts you to 20 results, rather than letting you scroll through all the filtered Likes. This is only an issue on the app as of the recent week or two. I submitted a support ticket, provided a recording showing the issue and was told, "Unfortunately, this is all the support we’re able to offer at this moment. We appreciate your time and understanding."', "Premium is pretty much worthless. The algorithm still treats you the same way. So you're essentially paying to swipe on profiles that wouldn't even see you. stick with the free version. It doesn't really improve the matches that much. Only real benefit for paying is it saves you some time you won't have to wait a few hours. Also if you are planning a vacation somewhere might help with the passport feature. Feel kinda ripped off to be honest.", "The functionality is basically gone. Swipes won't register, and once you swipe the first time, it shows you're out of swipes and keeps cycling through the same people but won't tell you that nothing is actually happening. I can message my old matches, but cannot view their profile and pics, any attempt will boot you out of the app. Changing distance and age range also has no effect, and changes won't save anyway. The constant ad profiles are garbage too, but at least that much is intentional.", 'I used to be able to easily remove myself from the stack. Now the setting to enable or disable the discovery feature is hidden and it tries to get you to pay for a premium feature instead of just turning off discovery. On top of that the setting has never changed for me no matter how many times I have gone into settings and turned off enable discovery. Being able to turn off tinder without deleting my profile was important to me. Will be looking at other apps.', 'Designed to waste money, customer support is trained to be unhelpful. "SUPERLIKES" are something you pay for. The app is designed to constantly shoot up a big pop up bubble to remind you to use it. If you accidentally touch that bubble, it automatically uses a superlike. You are supposed to get it back if you are a subscriber and "undo" the like immediately, but you do not. Support refuses to help. Tinder is a scam designed to bleed you for money.', 'Customer support is horrible. Constantly just copy and pasting the same thing over and over. Not actually communicating. No phone number for support either. I would buy the standard boosts and I would get prime time boosts instead. Also charged for them as well. They would run automatically while I was traveling. What a scam. Also unable to get verified. The new AI verification simply does not work no matter what I would do with lighting or anything else in their FAQs and CS responses.', "Overpriced, so many bots and fake profiles, you see the same profiles over and over again. No matches if you buy premium, but when it runs out, you suddenly get dozens of matches that you can't see, and so have to upgrade again. Basically, it's a big con to get you to spend money, and an apt representation of the soulless, superficial nature of modern dating.", 'Have had a lot of the "your account has been banned" notification. Even though I\'ve done nothing wrong and after uninstalling the app for a while it usually fixes it. But it\'s very frustrating not having access to my account. Customer service even said they see nothing wrong with y account on their end. But it shows it on multiple devices for me. Idk but it\'s VERY irritating.', "The past 2 days the app freezes during the sign up process. At the final screen where you select your interests, that screen is blank and you can go no further. I've tried uninstalling the app, cleaning up my phone memory/system. Reinstall and giving permissions to the app prior to first run. Still the same problem. Dunno what's going on, maybe something at your end, I've tried everything I can think of here. The app has worked perfectly for years until yesterday.", "Every dating app is the same, swipe left or right and bribes for spetial access making it generally a lower probability for a match to happen. Just this one also has a terrible interface designed to confuse and make mistakes as easily as possible. And of course we all agree on everything negative that's been said already. Design for failure. Oops you missed a match!", "I don't know what kind of engineers and testers you hired, many features are not working in your app. I've tried to get photo verified my account, but it showing something went wrong everytime. For that issue, I tried to attach a snapshot but that feature is also useless, that button is not responding. Pause your app in production and deep dive into that.", "This app could be good, and is under certain circumstances, but once you've messed up your algorithm no one will ever see you and you'll just be cursed to swiping endlessly on people that will never see your card on their stack. Also the premium features are nice but the price has increased exponentially to a point where I don't think I'd ever be able to financially justify even the lowest tier. Like a lot of apps, Tinder has only gotten worse and worse as time goes on.", "I NEVER GOT TO USE THE APP. Once I created a profile, I changed the settings and started to update my bio. As I was completing the About Me section, prompts came up asking if I was human then a screen saying that I'm banned and won't be able to reactivate the account. I never even got to use the account. The only thing I can think of is that using the option to block contacts triggered it. My photos and everything else weren't inappropriate. A waste of my time and sign not to be on this app.", 'Very limited features, they want you to pay for basic stuff. I get matches with people who I am sure I never liked . Matched me with same people 2-3 times. Doesn\'t show all people around me (I tested with friends). Shows 99+ liked me since last year but blocks and hides those profiles to force me to buy plus/gold version of the app. Once in a blue moon it shows a "secret admirer" but the last time it was a person with whom I had already matched and unmatched. Disappointment', "The app does next to nothing about the constant stream of fake accounts, likely because this gives you a seemingly high number of anonymous likes, which pressures you into buying premium to see them. (Which I've had from the start) For example, every day or so I would get a new like, from a new account, exactly 30 miles away. Dozens of these. The app isn't designed to find you matches. Its designed to string you along for as long as possible to keep you paying for it.", "Every time I open the app since downloading several days ago, I'm met with a screen to verify my profile with photos. When I go to take the photos, the buttons don't work meaning I can't actually verify my account. I can't use the app at all, not even to delete my profile. Support has been giving canned responses which don't actually address the issue. Kind of a bummer.", "The latest update has removed the option to hide your profile, so if you meet someone interesting the only option is to close your account completely instead of deactivating it while you see how things progress. Several days later and 'disable discovery' still doesn't work. The only option is to remove your photos and block payment. Finally, after two weeks it's been fixed.", "The app seems like a scam to me. I paid for the gold membership and I stopped getting likes. Once it ran out, the likes started coming again. The gold membership is pointless, it just gives you unlimited likes and allows you to see who liked you and constantly presses you to upgrade to platinum. The app seems to drip feed you the matches, just enough to keep you engaging and liking other profiles. I wouldn't waste your time paying for it. If you use it for a couple of months you get free matches", 'Practically unusable - gets stuck on "Finding people near you" and other tabs don\'t load content either. The content does eventually load bit by bit, taking multiple minutes for each tab. Images then take even more time to load in, sometimes never actually loading. Other apps don\'t have the same issue and speed tests don\'t show any issues. Edit: no way to undo an accidental swipe without paying. Overall frustrating experience.', "Easily the worst dating app I've used, go find a competitor. I've had plenty of matches and successful dates on other platforms, but Tinder has only ever resulted in a few dead-end matches. And it's not hard to see why. There's no recommendation algorithm, it's just a firehose of low effort profiles which have nothing in common with you. They have a page which gives you a couple of loose categories, but then they kneecap it by hiding important parts of a user's profile for no damn reason.", 'No matches unless you upgrade. Then you\'re getting secret admirers that you already received before. So you\'re basically paying for the same thing, over and over. Also, you have to remove your payment method when you sign up for the upgrades because if you simply "cancel" the upgrade with how the app functions right now, it won\'t work and you\'re going to be getting charged.', 'Weird. This app I\'ve used for only 4 days and for some reason after 3 days of talking to a person that person all of a sudden doesn\'t message back and only new matches seem to respond. And as soon as youbtjink that you\'re going to "click" with someone all of a sudden they\'re gone from your messages. All of a sudden too in the middle of me messaging back to someone all.of a sudden the entire conversation disappears. This app is rigged and controlled. Happened with every single person I messaged.', "If the app is running slow or not responding, try switching from WIFI to Data on your phone. It makes a huge difference for me even though my WiFi is supposed to be faster than data. Not a bad app in terms of user interface and better than many others in this regard. The content might or might not appeal to everyone's needs/taste but this is a reflection of the social environment.", "Practically broken. Every message I send gives me an error or crashes. Spent 45 minutes trying to talk to a match only to have the system fail every time I try. Restart doesn't fix, reinstall makes it worse. Considering it's already designed to be as ineffective as possible this is basically my last straw.", "Super intrusive ads. I get sent push notifications constantly. I can't turn them off because then I won't receive notifications for messages from actual matches. Their monetization model is predatory. Intrusive ads don't stop even if you buy the mid tier option (which is expensive at 15€ a month). Very bad value for what you get. Oh and to get the full experience, without ads etc, you need to pay 35€ a month. Sure, Jan, let me get my checkbook.", "New account, updated profile and pics, everything was supposed to work but out of the blue - banned. And then started working again, purchased platinum and still nothing works. Same people keeps appearing and even if liked, they doesn't appear in the Likes Sent section. Happening to almost all as I can see in these recent reviews of the application, this is just not is expected. I am waiting to see if they can fix it.", "It won't allow me to delete my account! When I click on the option, I'm directed to a screen asking if I'm sure, etc., but there's no button I can click to delete it. I even updated the app, but it's still the same. Tinder has reached a new low! Edit: 3 days later and the issue in the app still persists! I managed to delete my account only through a browser.", '"face to face time" doesn\'t seem to work. At least not in my country. And yes I reinstalled the app and checked connection issues. This is a "safety breach". It requires other apps and disclosure of unwanted personal information to see who you\'re talking to. In the event that users might be disconnecting calls willingly, I would suggest a more informed notification like: "user so and so has disconnected the call" so that one can opt to Unmatch fake profiles and other time waste attempts.', "Not worth paying for. Ive been swiping for ages and paid for additional benefits thinking I'll have more chances. But free version and paid version will still feel the same cause chances are still slim both ways. Only been match with 3. Only one replied but that one didn't work out. So still searching and no real good outcomes. Paid for bumble. I think chances there are better. Been matched to 17 people there already. Almost all replies too. Tinder aint working as it's suppose to. Lipat nalang."]

title: Cute Dog's Life
description:
Explore the world of Puzzles with cute pet Dogs! Easy, swift, fun to play Puzzle game.♪
Take care of all your pets along with progressing through tons of unique stages!

Easy, fun to play Puzzle Game with virtual pet Dogs!
Download Dog Life for FREE!
No annoying registration required! Intuitive interface! 

Enjoy solving easy, fun puzzles with pet dogs!
Take care of your pet dogs, solve Puzzles together!
Stages get harder as you progress, everyone from a Beginner to an Expert can enjoy! Absolutely FREE!

Come, experience an Adventure with cute pet Dogs!
Cute doggies such as puppies and toy poodles, miniature dachshunds, pomeranian, chihuahua etc. appear.

★How to play
☆Connect three or more coins!
Special coin appears on connecting many coins at once!

☆Different stages have different requirements!
Satisfy mentioned requirements to clear the stage!
Keep in mind the time limit and the number of moves left!

☆Clear stages to get new pets!
Your new pet will appear in the Garden!

☆Refresh yourself by spending quality time with cute pets!
Pet your dogs, feed them, and even play Fetch!
Personalize the garden area as per your liking! Transform it into your own personal space!

☆Special Events Planned!
Get exclusive pet dogs during special events! Such events will keep on happening!

☆World Ranking System!
Compete with players all around the world on the basis of your Star Count, i.e. Star Ranking.
There's also an event exclusive Event Ranking system! 
Event Ranking toppers will receive special presents on event completion!
summary:
★Puzzle game with cute pet Dogs★
Easy, swift, fun to play Puzzle game♪

title: Old Friends Dog Game
description:
Welcome to Old Friends Dog Game, where love never grows old! Create your own dog sanctuary in this heartwarming pet rescue simulator. Rescue adorable senior dogs and uncover their life story as you shower them with love. Decorate with cute doggy decor, bake scrumptious dog snacks, and experience the joy of helping cute senior dogs live out their golden years in the best way possible. 

Inspired by the real life pet residents at Old Friends Senior Dog Sanctuary, these cute dogs have heartwarming stories and personalities that you'll uncover as you rescue them and provide the care they need to live their best dog life!

Awarded Gold winner at the 2022 NYX Awards, a finalist for Pocket Gamer's Game of the Year, and a Webby honoree for Social Impact in Games, this cute dog simulator is a must-play!

Gameplay:

❤️ Meet the town residents and rescue cute senior dogs. Help them live their best life by fulfilling their needs and ensuring their happiness. As you feed, pet, and play with your dogs, their love and loyalty grows.

📘 Choose how the story unfolds. In this dog simulator, you pick the path for each dog's story! Unlock multiple chapters for every cute doggy you rescue.

💒 Customize your dog sanctuary and make it a haven for your dogs. Decorate indoors and outdoors with cute doggy decor that will make your dogs feel right at home!

🧁 Bake lip-smacking treats for your beloved dogs, ensuring they never go hungry.

🧣 Dress up your dogs in cute pet outfits! Each dog has adorable accessories that you can earn.

🐕 Give your dog sanctuary the personal touch - feature a custom profile, a unique avatar, and a gallery of cute photos of each dog!

**********

Old Friends Dog Game is developed and published by Runaway.

This game is free to play but does contain some items available to purchase for real money. If you run into any issues while playing or you have any suggestions, please reach out to us at support@runaway.zendesk.com. OLD FRIENDS DOG SANCTUARY™ is made by Runaway Play.
summary: Save cute dogs and help them enjoy life in this pet rescue simulator!

comments: ["I played the game a while ago and recently reinstalled it, but now it won't even let me past level one. Everytime I try to stream it just makes the screen go black, and nothing happens. I've tried everything to fix it, reinstalling again, restarting my phone, even went online to try and find an answer. Love the game, just wish I could get further with it.", "A lot of potential! As others have said, minigames would be nice like washing, playing, and brushing dogs. An issue I've run into just today is the ads crashing the game afterwards, losing the reward. My daily dig actually fully vanished after I hit the watch ad button and the game crashed, I can't even pay tickets for another. Also had to play through a level-up livestream twice due to the ad issue, did not get rewards.", "Absolutely loving the game so far! I'm relieved it's not another match 3 or merge 2 games, and really is about taking care of old dogs and managing the sanctuary. I've seen the game's advert for a long time, I regret not playing it sooner. But better now than never I guess! Only thing is the game keeps crashing on me occasionally while loading a new scene (ex; getting a new dog, loading livestream, .etc) I love the game and I want to support the funding, I'd appreciate a smoother experience. :')", "I absolutely love this game! It's adorable, and I haven't experienced any bugs (I have played for about a month now). Though, for the Dog Blog, there are limited color options, which, as someone with bright green hair, is a little saddening :( Aside from my dramatics about hair color, I recommend everyone give this game a try! It's so customized, and each dog has their own favorite treats and toys, which is so fun to memorize. I love this game!!", "This game is really amazing and I love the style so much! I really like the game because it's supporting a real life senior dog sanctuary too! But last 3 or 4 days I couldn't get in the game because i got a message about some kind of error and I tried everything to get rid of it but it hasn't been working so far. I got pretty good progress there so it's going to be sad if i lose it. I don't know if its a game error or its like that for someone too but I hope it gets fixed soon!", "Very Cute very relaxing it's really wholesome too! But, I've been having issues lately When I stream the screen becomes black and the music keeps playing and I can't go to the next level because my first time of streaming is glitching I've been having Issues with that so whatever you could do please Fix it....", "First things first, this is not a game you will play for an hour straight. More like a few minutes at a time. Gameplay is fun though. Little thing I mentioned pre-edit, So basically my progress reset, (It has been fixed now.) Devs should probably look into what caused that. Also I don't know if the message I sent to tell them it was fixed worked? All in all, great game, great devs. (What caused the game to reset though?)", "A awesome friendly game where you get to experience adventures and journey with these adorable dogs and the amazing artwork! I love this game. It's just heartwarming. And there is so much more potential to expand apon! The fact that it was based on real dogs and experiences is also amazing. You get to read snippets of real-world inspiration the further you progress.", "This is THE BEST chill/idle kind of game I've ever played. There's so much to do! You are always getting rewards constantly, even past the early game. There are only ads very rarely, when you want to increase your rewards. The dogs are so sweet and have personality that you uncover through their individual story lines. You'll fall in love. I had this game ages ago and left it like I always do with mobile games (I'm fickle lol) and this is the ONLY game I missed so much I had to come back again!", "This game is fun but I got stuck on the streaming stage Everytime I tried the screen would go black to the point I just left and rejoin the game and when I kept trying it took my stuff but never worked if u could see if it's a bug please update Soo it doesn't happen to other people", "it was almost an amazing game, except for the fact that it was lacking in furniture and decoration aspects. it's fun caring for the dogs, but i wish i could put more furnitures. there's so many furniture blueprints, but i cant craft becuz the materials for good furnitures are so hard to get. i wish we could buy materials from donations, or we could get from streams. idk. im quite unsatisfied witht the reward rn", "This make me cry so much. I love idle games. I love that this is based off an actual doggy sanctuary with the actual doggies and with pictures of the actual doggies attached. I'm sad and happy and my heart melt. Some lags and bugs are experienced and the game crashes too. But i just love the concept of this game. Good strategy to make ppl adopt senior dogs and cry cause they're gone too soon", "It's really great especially for dog lovers! I Love it a lot and especially that it's also a real sanctuary.. It really makes me wanna donate now :( but my parents do not allow me sadly... I hope some people will still donate :) definitely will recommend some friends to play this..!", "Old friends dog adventure is such a fun game where you care for older dogs and play the challenges! You get to choose what to say and there's even a dog blog! Definitely would recommend.", 'Sancuaty names could be more customizable(wanted to name mine after my old pup, Timber.) But otherwise, The game is amazing. The graphics are great. The dogs are adorable. And I love the hat for Mack.', 'Absolutely what I was looking for in a game, perfect with little to no ads and with very reasonable microtransactions! Would recommend', "Very cute! I would love if the game would emphasize the importance of identifying dog-friendly costumes that won't bother dogs vs coatumes that will make them uncomfortable all day, but overall its super fun 👍", "THIS GAME IS THE ACTUAL BEST! BAGEL IS SO CUTE MACK IS SO CUTE AND LEO IS SO CUTE,there's so many things to do!Decorate your sanctuary,collect new dogs,and it's all so much fun I love the theme and design of the game and how they're based on real life senior dogs!I wish I could meet them in real life!I was quite sad when I found out they only sold the merchandise in USD cuz I'm from the UK but seriously if I could I'd give this game a million bigillion stars out of a million biggilion stars!☆", "I am only on 3rd level, and I think it is really fun, cute, and great for a dog lover. I do find it a bit repetitive, but that will probably change over time. I olso do think Runaway's other games are really good too. If you delete their games, your progress will not be saved, though.", 'This game is so cute and entertaining! The dogs are adorable. Even the situations where almost nothing is going on it is really fun. Just baking food or cleaning the house just makes you feel happy and calm. I love this game and I really recommend this game for all dog lovers! ❤️', "It's such a cute game about dogs and don't love a dog for its age love it forever no matter what because old dogs are cute too and in the game you can unlock cute dogs like mack and bagel and Leo there so adorable doesn't matter how old a dog is love lasts for eternity I love Leo Babs and Captain Ron too runaway pls update maybe fix the bugs? Not asking for much ty the bug is it takes a bit to load and sometimes when I try saving a picture it says contact support game kicks me out any way to fix", 'I feel good playing with old friends, . I recently had to start a new game over because old friends got accidentally erased , I was devastated. Old friends helps me cope with losing my old friend scrappy. He was my everything, he passed away not long ago he was 16 and so loved. Thank you old friends for reaching out and I was very excited to hear from you. Thank you old friends.', 'This Is such a heartwarming game, I love how simple are the interactions with the dogs. I love the little stories that they include of the dogs adapting to their new home. Amazing game!', 'This game is just so adorable, and the fact that it is based on real life dogs just makes it 10 times more interesting and unique! Love it, keep up the great work. ( I also totally recommend!)', 'This game is adorable and I love the concept of it. It is so cute and so fun, and i love that the dogs each have the personalities of the real pups. And favorite treats and toys. Babs is my favorite pupbso far hehe Ten stars from me!', 'Ohh, they have fixed the problem, the game is really wonderful, and very innovative, please I recommend you download it and give it a try', "So far, it's a really fun game! However I wish furniture was cheaper and there were more coupon codes. But overall, it's really good!", 'I love this game but my account got restarted and when i just wanted to play i was in the start again i dont know to get my stuff and my progress back please help i dont wanna start again.I still have the furniture that is needed coupons. But the ones i crafted is gone and the progress of the dogs are gone and i only have mack again', 'Edit: After 2 years of playing this game, it has become quite dull. The events are all repeats from the years prior... I already have all the rewards from the bake-offs, so why even participate? I have been at the max level for probably a year now. Not much to do after completing the stories. I have 3 senior rescues myself (2 dogs and 1 cat), so this game is perfect for me. I recently applied to vet school and want to focus on old animals. This game is everything I want out of life!!!', 'One of the first times a mobile game has truly felt like a game. Love oozes from every millimeter of this experience. Even the ads are non-intrusive, and from what I understand completely optional. Highly recommend!', 'Game has reset on me twice, erasing all my progress. The first time I used recover to get back to my original game. The second time it reset, I tried to recover my original game, but only the two previous reset games appear, making me start with zero progress. If this is not fixed, I will never play this again.', "Super cute and makes me feel better about playing mind-numbing games that get me nowhere. The only complaint I have is that the app randomly restarts sometimes after an ad video. Also, videos have been unavailable for me all day so I can't get Mack his chicken flavoring 🥹", "Love the premise behind the game and was enjoying playing it. The dog message requests bugged out with no images and did nothing when I clicked on them so I rebooted the game and it lost all my data :( I'm scared it will happen again.", 'This game is so much fun, and although you have to work very hard, the dogs are soo cute. Most relaxing game ever!', "It is amazing there's lots of adventures the dogs are so cute but the best thing is getting more of the dog's stories.", "This is a cute game and I enjoy it but I can't progress past the streaming part as the screen just goes black.", 'So far this is super cute and fun. a little bit slow, but really heartwarming and relaxing.', "Cute little game. I haven't closed it since download because I'm mildly afraid of missing things when my attention differs, but that's the only issue and isn't even really one! The whole app is so fun and adorable that I can't keep my hands off of it 🙈", "I don't know why it's taken me so many years to download a wholesome game about dogs. So far into the game, it's easy to follow, lovely story and beautiful graphics. If you love dogs and want causal gameplay, this should suit you:)", "Love this game; it's so nice and wholesome! There has been issues with my progress resetting, but whenever that happens I breeze through the intro sequence then contact support through the game's settings, and they fix it in like a day. One thing I really wish the game had though is the ability to replay cutscenes, because the stories are just really cute."]

title: Hundeo: Puppy & Dog Training
description:
🐶 Dog & Puppy Training Made Easy 🐕
Don't have a dog trainer or puppy training school with you right now? No problem! Hundeo offers you step-by-step video instructions on the most important topics that a digital dog obedience school can offer you in your pocket. We guide you from puppy to senior with the right content.

300+ Tricks, Games, Recipes and Courses.
Discover a wide range of tricks, games, and recipes for dogs. Get inspiration for your next training session and have fun together. In this app, you can find for example these course topics: Basic Commands, Puppy Basics (Walking the Pup, Potty House Training, Bite inhibition, Puppy Nutrition, Puppy Games, Puppy Commands), Leash Training, Recall Masterclass, How to ignore other dogs on walks, How to behave during a visit, Clicker Course, Dog Impulse control Guide, Health Check at Home, Raw Food Diet, Muzzle Trainer, Calm at Office, New Year's Eve Training, Stop your dog from eating random things, Stop Barking Trainer or Stay Alone Course for Dogs.

Step by Step to Your Goal
We guide you to your goal with our interactive video tutorials.
The tutorials are designed so that you can be successful with just 5 minutes of training a day. It reminds you of your training and when you train successfully, you get a great trophy for your virtual trophy case. In addition to dog training methods, you will also find great activities in the form of pet games and recipes.

Anytime, Anywhere - At Your Own Pace
Out in the park or garden with no reception? No problem. You can download content and use it offline.

New Daily
Daily free quizzes, tricks, games, recipes and courses carefully selected for you. Tailored to you and your breed. (We have 285 dog breeds like Labrador, French Bulldog, Pug, Doberman, Chihuahua)

Playfully to Success
To keep you motivated, you get new challenges every day and earn flames and trophies. 

Individual Profile
Create a profile for your puppy, dog, or even multiple pets and keep track of what you have accomplished and what you still need to practice.

Connect With Others
Have you learned some cool dog or puppy tricks and want to compare yourself with others? Invite your friends or other members of our community to compare your achievements and watch videos of other dogs and puppies.

Your Favorites
Keep track and create your own favorites list for easy access.

Clicker and Whistle Always With You
With a clicker, you always have the right tone with you. A clicker is the most efficient way to teach your puppy tricks and exercises.

Trusted
This app was developed in collaboration with professional dog experts and pet trainers. You can be sure that the exercises will really help you.

Support
If you have any questions about Hundeo or your account, please contact our customer support: support@hundeo.com

Hundeo Plus Membership
To unlock all the features, you can upgrade to ‘hundeo Plus’ and choose between the following subscriptions:
1 month
1 year

Terms and Conditions: https://www.hundeo.com/en/toc/
Privacy policy: https://www.hundeo.com/en/contact/data-protection/

comments: ["The app is pretty good and easy to work around. My only problem is that I have to be on a subscription or premium plan in order to access most of the stuff. People who go to apps for dog training don't really have the money, so they're not going to be able to go on to the premium plan to get access to most of the app. Other than that, it's a good app", "For weeks under maintenance, no training plans available Update: I was not using an old version but I have Adguard on my phone. Seems like the app does not work if it's routed through Adguard...", "I honestly enjoy this training tips it's extremely helpful to me .", 'easy to follow! works well', 'This looks like a really cool app, and I was very excited to use it with my twin cavapoo puppies. But I was dismayed that after I created an account it said that there were only 7 days of a free trial and then I would have to pay for the app and would be automatically billed for it. Beyond not impressed with this bait and switch for what is advertised as a free app. I deleted my account immediately, and I better not be charged in a week.', "I just downloaded & has all the selections of different trainings, tips & tricks. looks like alot of information needed ..HOWEVER, I am needing something to be done QUICK...instead of learning one tip or trick at a time.. it wants to give me ONE lesson one day at a time...I have a dog with separation anxiety & will not stop barking.. barks all night & throughout the day at times.PLEAAE HELP.... I'm still trying other apps as well for the dog barking..whistling apps etc.. I can't afford the prem", 'fun and easy!', "Good app but my dog won't listen to me when I teach her high-five she only listen to me when it's paw or games,☹️", 'Epic I just downloaded I tryed to get her to lie down but she just looked down but well work on it.', "Not Free at all!!! Advertised as free but the only 'free' part is an introduction to each lesson, the introduction only tells you what you will get out of that lesson and gives no advice at all. Don't waste your time unless you want to pay.", 'I tried it with my dog and definitely got results, the tricks and games are great fun for my doggy and honestly cheap for a year of home-training!', 'I love the great video collection. It is also good that there are not only educational videos but also about dog health.', 'Simple, easy to follow tips and tutorials. Helped me finally to get my puppy to sit and control those impulses!', "so far the app is very helpful, Roxie has already picked up on 2 new tricks! She's such a smart little girl!", 'Good free version', 'Very good and helpful I have a young dog and have long been looking for a solution that helps. I really like the step-by-step video tutorials.', 'wow it taught my dog to stay when I went some where yet he has separation anxiety wow thanks', 'it really helped me trane my dog not that good, but it is not the app it is the dog🥰', 'Amazing app should use for sure only thing you need to pay it would be amazimg to gave it for free for some people it would be really useful', "my dog is a puppy and she doesn't now any tricks so I need help", 'tried free version for 7 days, forgot about it and they charged me not even month but for 1 year. Looks like scum.', 'Great for teach dogs tricks,and great recipes so over all brilliant app(my fav trick was little heart♡♡)', "Very nice app but one thing I don't like that is there is not Indian spitz bread option.I hope you will add it.", "DO NOT DOWNLOAD. THE APP DOESN'T WORK MOST OF THE TIME. ONCE YOU SUBSCRIBE YOU CAN'T CANCEL IT. IT'LL CHARGE YOU EVERY MOUTH AND THERE IS NO WAY TO GET OUT OF IT.", 'I recommend this app because it teaches your dog commands that you want them to listen to and it also help my dog sit shake and pound it which is a good thing', "Couldn't even get started. Just got to the setup your account and even after I did, didn't move on to the next stage.", 'The right thing for me as a dog owner Very well-developed app for dog owners. A well done app. I like it.', 'Installed in German . Could not change to English Language', "anyway we can get Great Pyrenees tips and tricks?!? found my lab, river, profile but can't set up my charlie bears just yet bc there isn't a bread set up for him yet.", 'wonderful app! Thank you so much, it taught my dog, Doc, how to stay', 'It has amazing trick ideas and amazing healthy recipes for your dog 🐶🐕🐩🐶🐕🐩🐕🐶', 'so good helps my dog learn so many new things', "It's nice but there was no breed option for English shepherd i hope you add that someday", 'Not able to login. Some error popping up', 'I know this is The only review but trust me,this is The Best app ever! My dog learned so much tricks from there!😻😻❤️\u200d🩹', 'The app looks good , i only gave it 4 stars because I have not used the training methods on my 4 dogs yet but I will try it tomorrow.', "Save yourself some money. There's far BETTER programs out there.", 'good for most parts🙂', 'This good is very very interesting ☺️ and I am very happy to using this app 😊 and dog too thankyou so much', "Very good app I love it but I tried making a profile for my dad's dog but there's no American bulldog but my dog works he is a pug"]
